\c 1
\s UYohana uMutwiniaji iikhoma ku lunyikha
\r (Mataayo 3:1-12; Luuka 3:1-18; Yohana 1:19-28)
\p
\v 1 Ishi shiyanso sha Mola iNofu iya Yeesu Kilisito,\f + \fr 1:1 \fq Kilisito: \ft Liswi lya Shiyunaani. Kwa Shihebulaniya viija \fqa Mesiya\fqa*. Yimba iliswi \fqa Kilisito\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* Lusawo lwa Nguluvi.\f + \fr 1:1 \fq Lusawo lwa Nguluvi: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f*
\v 2 Injowo sayansaaga ngaja shina yiyandiikhwe mu litaafili lya mukuwamalago uIsaaya. UNguluvi wájovile,
\b
\q “Loleela, nikimufilikha umunjaajila wangu
\q yuna akhakulongola kumwandi.
\q Uyo yumwene yuna akhakunosesa insila yaakho.”\f + \fr 1:2 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Malaaki 3:1.\f*
\q
\v 3 “Ishawuti ya muunu yipuliisikha mu lunyikha yiija,
\q ‘Mumunosesaaje uMutwa\f + \fr 1:3 \fq UMutwa: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Mutwa\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* insila yaakwe
\q na kimugolosesa muna akhashila.’\f + \fr 1:3 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Isaaya 40:3. \f*”
\b
\p
\v 4 Umunjaajila yula yu Yohana Mutwiniaji. Wáhumiliile ku lunyikha, iikhoma imola iija, avaanu valambiisile uwunansi waanave na kitwinisiwa, baheene uNguluvi avasaajile.
\v 5 Avaanu kihuma ku lijumbi lya Yelusalemu\f + \fr 1:5 \fq Yelusalemu: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* na ku mbali soona isa nyi ya Yudeya, vamulutiile uYohana. Vakhandi vilambiisila uwunansi waanave, woope akhandi ikivatwinia mu mukhoga gwa Yolodani.
\p
\v 6 Amenda ga Yohana gakhandi gatendiilwe kwa waaji wa ngamiya, akhandi ikiyipinya ulukhova lwa nkwembe mu shigudi\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Umwenda guna akhandi ifwala uYohana, gukhandi guhwaneene nu mwenda ugwa mukuwamalago uEliya. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya 2 Vatwa 1:8.\f* na kiilya inkumbi nu wuushi uwa mu lihakha.
\v 7 Baheene uYohana akhandi iikhoma iija, “Kunyuma yangu iyinsa uyunji, umunya ngufu kishila one, yuna nisikwiliile kiiva muvanda waakwe wa kigondama na kihudula ingalawo sa ndaatu saakwe.
\v 8 One nikivatwinia kwa malenga, leelo umwene akhavatwinia kwa Numbula uMunofu.”\f + \fr 1:8 \fq Numbula uMunofu: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f*
\s UYeesu itwinisiwa na kijelwa
\r (Mataayo 3:13–4:11; Luuka 3:21-22; 4:1-13)
\p
\v 9 Uluhaavi ulo, pina uYohana itwiniaga, uYeesu wáhumile ku lijumbi lya Nasaleti ku nyi ya Galilaya, wálutile ku mukhoga gwa Yolodani, kiija atwinisiwe nu Yohana.
\v 10 UYeesu wáganile kitwinisiwa, baaho hela wáganile kihuma mu malenga, wáawona uwulanga widindukha, nayu Numbula uMunofu iyiikha pamwene kwa shihwano sha nkunda.
\v 11 Baheene iliswi lyapuliisikha kihuma kushaanya liija, “Owe yuuwe Lusawo lwangu, nikugeene na ukinishendeefya.”
\p
\v 12 Baaho uNumbula uMunofu wámulungamyaga uYeesu kiluta ku lunyikha.
\v 13 Wákheele ukho nsiku mashumi gana, kuno uShetaani\f + \fr 1:13 \fq UShetaani: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Shetaani\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* akhandi ikimujela. Wáali lumo ni nkhanu, na vamalayikha\f + \fr 1:13 \fq Vamalayikha: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Malayikha\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* va Nguluvi vaava vikimusunga.
\s UYeesu ikivabaagula avamanyisiwa ava wutasi
\r (Mataayo 4:12-22; Luuka 4:14-15; 5:1-11)
\p
\v 14 Kuunyuma, uYohana uMutwiniaji wádindiilwe mu shifungo, uYeesu wálutile ku Galilaya kikhoma iMola iNofu isa Nguluvi.
\v 15 Wájeele kiija, “Uluhaavi luna lwatahisiwaagwa nu Nguluvi lwafikha. Khanji uWutwa wa Nguluvi\f + \fr 1:15 \fq UWutwa wa Nguluvi: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Wutwa wa Nguluvi \ft mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* wahejeela kunyeenyu. Mulambiisile uwunansi weenyu na kihuviilila iMola iNofu isa Nguluvi.”
\p
\v 16 UYeesu wáfikhaga ku lilamba ilikhome ilya Galilaya. Pina akhandi iishila mulubali, wávaajile avalova nswi uSimoni\f + \fr 1:16 \fq USimoni: \ft Paanyuma uYeesu wámupeelaga ilitaawa lya Petulo.\f* nu Andeleya umaame, vakhandi viilova inswi ni nyaafu.
\v 17 UYeesu wávashemeelile wávajovela, “Munifwataje, kiyansisa lino nikivapeela insengo iya kilova avaanu.”\f + \fr 1:17 \fq Kilova avaanu: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, kivakhoma avaanu iMola iNofu na kivagaha vamuhuviilile uYeesu. \f*
\v 18 Baaho vasilekha inyaafu saanave vayansa kimufwata.
\p
\v 19 UYeesu wálutile pamwandi padoodo, wávaajile uYaakobo nu Yohana avashina Sebedayo, vaali mu shipugo shaanave viinosa inyaafu saanave isa kilovela inswi.
\v 20 Baaho wávashemeela, vawuukha vamulekha uwihaanave uSebedayo mu shipugo, wáali na vasenga nsengo vaakwe, vamufwata uYeesu.
\s UYeesu ikilidaga ililungu limuhume umuunu
\r (Luuka 4:31-37)
\p
\v 21 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe awo, vaatile ku lijumbi lya Kapelinawumu. Lyaganile kifikha ilijuva lya Sabaato\f + \fr 1:21 \fq Sabaato: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* valutile mu nanda iya kifuunyila,\f + \fr 1:21 \fq Nanda iya kifuunyila: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* umo mumwene wáyansaaga kimanyisa.
\v 22 Avaanu woona vina vakhandi mula vaswijile mandu. Kiiva uYeesu asikhandi imanyisa ngaja avamanyisaaji vaanave ava ndaji sa Musa,\f + \fr 1:22 \fq Avamanyisaaji vaanave ava ndaji sa Musa: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa \ft mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* leelo wámanyisaaga ngaja muunu munya wutawulilwa.
\p
\v 23 Uluhaavi ulo, mu nanda ya kifuunyila, akhandi akwali umuunu umunya lilungu.
\v 24 Umuunu uyo wákhoolile inkhoolo mandu wáaja, “Wisakula shi kunyeesu, owe Yeesu wa ku Nasaleti? Uyinsile kitunanganga? Nimeenye kiija owe uli Munofu kihuma kwa Nguluvi.”
\v 25 UYeesu wálikhajila ililungu wáaja, “Sisima! Muhuma umuunu uyu!”
\v 26 Baheene ililungu lila lyamudegensa degensa umuunu yula, lyalyova kwa shawuti nkhome, lyamuhuma.
\p
\v 27 Avaanu woona vina vaali pala vaswijile mandu, vaposeenie vaajova, “Isi njowo nshi? Imanyiso isi mya, sina ngufu! Khanji ikigadaga amalungu goope gikimutiila!”
\v 28 Ndeeno imola sa Yeesu, sayalaliile nyangu nyangu uluvala loona ulwa nyi ya Galilaya.
\s UYeesu ikivaponia avatamu vinshi
\r (Mataayo 8:14-17; Luuka 4:38-41)
\p
\v 29 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe, uSimoni, uAndeleya, uYaakobo nu Yohana, vahumile mu nanda iya kifuunyila, valutile shiluta mbakha ku nanda ya Simoni nu Andeleya.
\v 30 Pina vafishile pala, baaho vamujoveele uYeesu kiija, umukweye uwa shidala uwa Simoni mutamu insegema, agonile pa wusaga.
\v 31 UYeesu wávejeelile pa mutamu, wámukhata iliwokho, wámunyenyula. Luhaavi luulo insegema yamuleshela, wáyansa kivasunga.
\p
\v 32 Lyaganile kisota ilijuva, pashaamihe avaanu woona ava mu lijumbi lila, vamuleteele avatamu na vanya malungu.
\v 33 Vakungaanile pa mulyango gwa nanda yila, muna wáali uYeesu.
\v 34 UYeesu wávaponiaga avatamu woona, vina vaali na matamu minshi paayo paayo na kigadaga amalungu minshi. Asikhagatawuliile kilogola hata padoodo, kiiva gaali gamumeenye, leelo umwene asikhandi idobokha avaanu vamumanye.
\s UYeesu ifuunya mwene duguli pashipata
\r (Luuka 4:42-44)
\p
\v 35 Ulwamilaawu njine pina kusinahenje kunena, uYeesu wálamwishe, wáwuukha iiluta pashipata, pina pangaya vaanu, apo wáfuunyile.
\v 36 USimoni na vayine valutile kimusakula.
\v 37 Vaganile kimwaga vamujoveele kiija, “Avaanu woona vikikusakula.”
\v 38 UYeesu wáaja, “Tilute mu njinji sina sili nkholeela, koope nikhome iliswi. Ulu lulwene luna nayinsila, kikhoma iliswi na kiponia imbali soona.”
\v 39 Baheene wálutile mu nyi yoona iya Galilaya, wákhomile iliswi mu nanda saanave isa kifuunyila isa Vayahuudi, na kidaga amalungu.
\s UYeesu ikimuponia umunya nyawulova
\r (Mataayo 8:1-4; Luuka 5:12-16)
\p
\v 40 Uluhaavi lumonga umuunu umunya nyawulova, wáyinsile kwa Yeesu, wáfugama, wámulomba wáaja, “Nda widobokha, nilomba univalase.”
\v 41 UYeesu wámusungupiile wágolosa iliwokho lyakwe wámupyasa\f + \fr 1:41 \fq Wámupyasa: \ft Kwa Vayahuudi yikhandi mwikho kimupyasa umunya nyawulova. Umuunu nda amupyase, yikhandi mwikho kiluta kimufuunya uNguluvi. \f* wámujova wáaja, “Nidobokha, uvalale.”
\v 42 Luhaavi luulo inyawulova yawushile mu muvili gwakwe, wávalala.
\v 43 Baaho pina akhandi ikimuwuusa umuunu yula, uYeesu wámukhaana wáaja,
\v 44 “Usikhajelaga kimujovela muunu yoyoona imola isi! Lino, lutaga uyiwonense kwa mutambule.\f + \fr 1:44 \fq Lino, lutaga uyiwonense kwa mutambule: \ft Kilingana ni ndaji sa Musa, umutambule yumwene akhandi iijinia kiija, umuunu wáapona inyawulova. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Njowo sa Valaawi 14:1-32; Luuju lwa Ndaji 24:8. \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Vatambule\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* Khanji, uhumye ishadanda isha kiwonensa kiija waapona, ngaja shina yiijova indaji ya Musa.”
\p
\v 45 Leelo umuunu uyo asawuyile asisime, wáwuushile wáyansiise kiyalaalisa imola iya kivalala umwene. Kilingana ni njowo iso, uYeesu wágombwele kihuluta mu majumbi pina avaanu vikimwaga, kiiva avaanu vamuyinsilaga kwa winshi. Leelo akhandi akheele kunja kulubali. Koope ukho ifipuga fya vaanu, kihuma imbali soona vamulutilaga umwene.
\c 2
\s UYeesu munya wutawulilwa wa kisaajila uwunansi
\r (Mataayo 9:1-8; Luuka 5:17-26)
\p
\v 1 Insiku nyasilinga ndeeni saganile kishila, uYeesu wátinile khanji mu lijumbi lya Kapelinawumu. Avaanu vapuliishe kiija uYeesu wáatina.
\v 2 Avaanu vinshi vakungaanile mu nanda muna wáali akwali uYeesu, vamemile mandu mukhati na pa mulyango hata mwenshe iya kihuluta yisikhawoneeshe. Uluhaavi ulo uYeesu akhandi apiikhoma iLiswi lya Nguluvi.
\v 3 Baheene vayinsa avaanu vana (4), vamusumwile umuunu yuna atengelemwishe umuvili.
\v 4 Leelo vagombwele kimuyinjisa pina akwali uYeesu kwa kiiva avaanu vakhandi vamemile mandu. Baheene vataanile pashaanya pa nanda vayansiise kidowola ulwansa, uwiima wuna akhandi akwali uYeesu. Vamuyinjisa baaho, akhandi agonile pa lupaasa.\fig |WA03824b.jpg|span|||Umuunu umutamu vikimuyiisa mu nanda|2:4\fig*
\v 5 UYeesu pina wályajile ilihuuvi lyanave, wámujovile umutamu yula, “Wee lusawo lwangu, wasaajilwa uwunansi waakho.”
\p
\v 6 Avaanu vamonga mu vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa vakhandi vakwali pala. Vaganile kipulikha iliswi ilyo, vahiivile vajeele,
\v 7 “Kwashi uyu iijova akwiliile kisaajila uwunansi? Umwene ikimutofola uNguluvi. Kusiina umuunu yuna akwiliile kisaajila uwunansi leelo yu Nguluvi mwene duguli.”
\v 8 Baaho uYeesu wámanyile luna vaali vihiiva mu numbula saanave, wávajovile, “Kwashi muhiiva ndeeno mu numbula seenyu?
\v 9 Lino! Lili kwi lina lipeefu? Kimujova umunya kitengelemukha umuvili kiija, ‘Wasaajilwa uwunansi waakho,’ awu kiija, ‘Yiima, yitwikha umushekha gwakho, ujende’?
\v 10 Lino mumanye kiija, one Lusawo lwa Muunu\f + \fr 2:10 \fq Lusawo lwa Muunu: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* nitawuliilwe uwutawulilwa uwa kisaajila avaanu uwunansi mu nyi muno.” Baheene wámujovela umunya kitengelemukha umuvili,
\v 11 “Nikikujova, yiima! Yitwikha umushekha gwakho, ulutaje kukhaaya yaakho!”
\v 12 Baaho wáyiima, wáyitwikha umushekha gwakwe wáawuya, avaanu woona vapikimwaga. Vaswijile mandu, khanji vamusufya uNguluvi kiija, “Iliswi ili tisinalyaje kaa.”
\s UYeesu ikimushemeela uLaawi ave mumanyisiwa waakwe
\r (Mataayo 9:9-13; Luuka 5:27-32)
\p
\v 13 UYeesu wálutile, wáafikha khanji kulubali lwa lilamba ilikhome ilya Galilaya. Ishipuga sha vaanu shalutile kwa Yeesu, baheene umwene wáyansiise kivamanyisa iliswi.
\v 14 Wáwuushile pala wáshilile kulubali lwa lilamba ilikhome. Pina akhandi ijenda wámwajile uLaawi, umutofya khoodi\f + \fr 2:14 \fq Umutofya khoodi: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Vatofya khoodi\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* yumonga, umuswamuve wa Alufaayo, yuna wáali akheele mu nanda muna akhandi itofesa ikhoodi. UYeesu wámujovela wáaja, “Nifwataga.” ULaawi\f + \fr 2:14 \fq ULaawi: \ft Ilitaawa lyakwe ilinji \fqa Mataayo. \f* wáyiima, wáyansa kimufwata.
\p
\v 15 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe, valutile kiilya ishakiilya kwa Laawi. Avatofya khoodi vinshi na vanya wunansi vinshi, vina vaali vamufwatile uYeesu, vaali vakheele lumo nawo.
\v 16 Avamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa avamonga vina vakhandi Vafalisaayo\f + \fr 2:16 \fq Vafalisaayo: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* woope vaali pala. Vaganile kimwaga iilya na vanya wunansi na vatofya khoodi, baheene vavaposiise avamanyisiwa vaakwe kiija, “Kwashi iilya lumo na vatofya khoodi na vanya wunansi awo?”
\v 17 UYeesu wáganile kipulikha ago wávajovela wáaja, “Avaanu vina vasili vatamu vasikimusakula umuhusi, leelo avatamu vaveene vina vikimusakula. Nisiyinsile kivashemeela avaanu vina vikiyiwona kiija vagolofu, leelo niyinsile kivashemeela avaanu vina vikiyiwona kiija vanansi.”
\s Iliposo ilya kilekha kiilya
\r (Mataayo 9:14-17; Luuka 5:33-39)
\p
\v 18 Uluhaavi lula avamanyisiwa va Yohana uMutwiniaji na vamanyisiwa va Vafalisaayo yaali ngʼoma yaanave iya kilekha kiilya, kiiva vifuunyaga.\f + \fr 2:18 \fq Kilekha kiilya, kiiva vifuunyaga: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Kilekha kiilya\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* Ilisiku limonga avaanu vayinsile vamuposa uYeesu, “Kwashi avamanyisiwa va Yohana na vamanyisiwa va Vafalisaayo vihwesaga vasiilya, leelo avamanyisiwa vaakho kwashi vasiigaha ngaja vala?”
\v 19 UYeesu wájovile, “Wuli, vina vayaniilwe ku shiwungo sha noolana, pina vali nu munya shiwungo isho, vakwiliile kilekha kiilya? Luhaavi loloona pina vali nu munya shiwungo akwali, vasihwesaga kiilya.
\v 20 Leelo, sikhayinsa insiku sina vakhamuwuusa umunya shiwungo, baheene vakhalekha kiilya.
\p
\v 21 “Kusiina umuunu yuna itoola ishilakha ishipya na kihona mu mwenda umukuulu. Nda agahe ndeeno, ishilakha shilekhana nu mwenda, umwenda ugo gwideemukha mandu.
\v 22 Khanji kusiina umuunu yuna iviikha idivaayi imya mu fiiwo ifikuulu. Kiiva nda agahe ndeeno ifiiwo fideemukha, idivaayi yikunukha na ifiiwo finanjikha. Leelo, avaanu viviikha idivaayi imya mu fiiwo ifipya.”\f + \fr 2:22 \ft Mu shihwano ishi, imola sa pawukuulu, mamanyiso awu ngʼoma sa pawukuulu, leelo imola imya, mamanyiso amapya aga Yeesu. Avaanu nda viyinatila amamanyiso amakuulu na mapya, vakwiliile kigananga goona. Yimba iliswi \fqa Divaayi\fqa* mu Maswa aMahensa.\f*
\s UYeesu yumwene Mutwa wa lijuva lya Sabaato
\r (Mataayo 12:1-8; Luuka 6:1-5)
\p
\v 23 Ilijuva limonga ilya Sabaato uYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vakhandi viishila mu magunda ga ngano. Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vakhandi vijenda kuno videenya na kipulula amahoojo ga ngano.
\v 24 AVafalisaayo vina vaali pala vavaajile, vamuposiise uYeesu kiija, “Loleela, kwashi avamanyisiwa vaakho vikigasenga gina gakhaniilwe pa lijuva lya Sabaato?”\f + \fr 2:24 \fq Gina gakhaniilwe pa lijuva lya Sabaato: \ft Indaji sa Vayahuudi sikhandi sisikimutawula hata padoodo umuunu kideenya amahoojo aga ngano, mu mugunda gwa muunu uyunji (\xt Luuju lwa Ndaji 23:25\xt*). AVafalisaayo vakhandi vilalamikha, kwa kiiva, kideenya amahoojo aga ngano, vijovaga kiija vasenga insengo.\f*
\p
\v 25 UYeesu wávayankha wáaja, “Wuli, musinayimbe mu Mayandikhwa aManofu umutwa uDawudi na vayine shina vagahile, pina vakhandi ni njala?
\v 26 Uluhaavi luna akhandi uAbiyatali mutambule mukhome, uDawudi wáhulwite mu liheema lya Nguluvi wátoola wáalya na vayine amakhaate gina gakhandi gavishiilwe pa Nguluvi. Indaji sa Musa sikhandi sikivakhaana kiilya amakhaate ago, ila avatambule veene duguli.”\f + \fr 2:26 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya 1 Samweli 21:1-6.\f*
\v 27 UYeesu wájovaga ndeeni, “Avaanu vasikhavishiilwe kwa lugulumilo lwa lijuva lya Sabaato, leelo ilijuva lya Sabaato lyavikhwagwa kwa lugulumilo lwa vaanu.
\v 28 Mumanye kiija one Lusawo lwa Muunu, yuune Mutwa hata wa lijuva lya Sabaato.”
\c 3
\s UYeesu iiponia umuunu mu lijuva lya Sabaato
\r (Mataayo 12:9-14; Luuka 6:6-11)
\p
\v 1 Uluhaavi ulunji uYeesu wáyinjiile khanji mu nanda iya kifuunyila. Mu nanda mula, wáali akwali umuunu yumonga yuna akhandi ana liwokho lina likholoweeshe.
\v 2 AVafalisaayo vakhandi vikimusigama mandu uYeesu, vamwaje nda asimuponie umuunu yula mu lijuva lya Sabaato, awu asimuponia. Nda asimuponie, vapate insila ya kimusitaakha uYeesu.
\p
\v 3 UYeesu wámujovela umuunu yula umunya liwokho likholoweeshe wáaja, “Yinsa, uyiime paakhati naakhati.”
\v 4 Baheene wávaposiise aVafalisaayo vala, wáaja, “Indaji seesu sikitutawula kigaha shishi mu lijuva lya Sabaato? Kigaha inofu awu imbi? Kiwukulusa uwuumi awu kiwuyasa?” Leelo aveene vasikhalogwele lyolyona.
\v 5 UYeesu wávangʼalulila ameeho woona kwa nkhalasi, khanji wásugumilwa mu numbula yaakwe, kwa kiiva ya numbula saanave saali nyuumu. Baheene uYeesu wámujovela umuunu yula wáaja, “Golosa iliwokho lyakho.” Woope wágolosa iliwokho lyakwe, baaho lyapona.
\v 6 Baaho aVafalisaayo ava, vaganile kilwaga ulo, vahumile kunja lumo na vanandeje va mutwa uHelode,\f + \fr 3:6 \fq Vanandeje va mutwa uHelode: \ft Avaanu vina vakhandi vayimililaaji mu wutwa wa Helode uAntipa. Khanji vakhandi pansi yaakwe. Yimba iliswi \fqa Helode \ft mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* vapulinkhane shina vakhasa kimubuda uYeesu.
\s Avaanu vinshi vikimufwata uYeesu vapate kipona
\p
\v 7 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vayibagwile, vawuushile viiluta ku lilamba ilikhome. Ishipuga shikhome sha vaanu kihuma ku Galilaya na ku Yudeya shamufwatile kukula.
\v 8 Khanji avaanu vinshi vina vapuliishe imola sa nsengo sina wásenjile uYeesu, vaatile kunyaakwe kihuma ku Yelusalemu, ku Idumeya, ku mbali sa ku Tiilo na ku Sidoni, na ku mwambwa ya mukhoga gwa Yolodani.
\v 9 UYeesu wávajovile avamanyisiwa vaakwe kiija, vavejeese ishipugo, baheene akhale mula mukhati mu shipugo amanyise, kiiva avaanu vakhandi vikimuminyiilisa.
\v 10 UYeesu akhandi avaponiise avaanu vinshi, lulwene avatamu vinshi vamuminyiliise viilwa vamupyase.
\v 11 Avaanu vina vaali vakhatiilwe na malungu, pina gamwajile uYeesu, gavagwisiise pa magulu gaakwe, gakhoolaga gajovaga, “Owe yuuwe Lusawo lwa Nguluvi.”
\v 12 Leelo wávapavilaga kwa wukhali kiija vasikhayalalisaaga kiija umwene yu naani.
\s UYeesu ikivabaagula avamanyisiwa ishumi na vavili
\r (Mataayo 10:1-4; Luuka 6:12-16)
\p
\v 13 UYeesu wálutile wátaana ku shidunda, baheene wávashemeela avaanu vaaluta kwa mwene.
\v 14 Baheene wávabaagula ishumi na vavili, wávapeela ilitaawa ilya vanandeje,\f + \fr 3:14 \fq Vanandeje: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Mwanandeje\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* na kiija vakhale nu mwene na avafilishe kikhoma imola sa Nguluvi,
\v 15 khanji wávatawuliile uwutawulilwa uwa kidaga amalungu.
\v 16 Avamanyisiwa ishumi na vavili vina wávabagwile uYeesu, vaveene ava, uSimoni (yuna uYeesu wámupeelaga ilitaawa lya Petulo),
\v 17 uYaakobo nu Yohana avaana va Sebedayo vina uYeesu wávapeelile ilitaawa lya Bowanelege. Uluganulo lwa Bowanelege, lusawo lwa lugulumo.
\v 18 Khanji wávabagwile uAndeleya, uFilipo, uBatolomaayo, uMataayo, uTomasi, uYaakobo umushina Alufaayo, uTadaayo, uSimoni uMulwila Nyi,\f + \fr 3:18 \fq UMulwila Nyi: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Mukananaayo\fqa*. Uluganulo lwakwe, \fqa uMulwila Nyi.\f*
\v 19 nu Yuuda uIsikaliyoote yuna kuwudugo wámudolelaga uYeesu.
\s UYeesu nu Belisebuli
\r (Mataayo 12:22-32; Luuka 11:14-23; 12:10)
\p
\v 20 Baheene uYeesu wáatile ikhaaya yina wáali afishiile lumo na vamanyisiwa vaakwe. Khanji avaanu vinshi vamukunganiliile. Avaanu vamemile mandu, uYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vaali vikivatanjilisaaga avaanu vala, lulwene vakunyile na kiilya.
\v 21 Avanyalukholo va Yeesu vapuliishe ku vaanu kiija, ahansinkheene uluhala, valutile kimutoola.
\v 22 Avamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa ku Yelusalemu vina vakhandi pala vaajova, “UYeesu ana Belisebuli,\f + \fr 3:22 \fq Belisebuli: \ft Litaawa ilinji lya Shetaani yuna mukhome wa malungu goona.\f* umukhome wa malungu, ililungu ilyo lilyene lina likimupeela ingufu isa kigadaga amalungu ku vaanu.”
\p
\v 23 UYeesu wávashemeelile avamanyisaaji vala, wálogola nawo kwa kihwananisa wáaja, “UShetaani akwiliile wuli, kiyidaga yumwene?
\v 24 Avaanu va wutwa wumo nda vatovane, uwutwa uwo wunanjikha.
\v 25 Hata mu litembe shiisho ndeeno, nda vanangane, ilitembe linanjikha.
\v 26 Shilushwali, nayu Shetaani nda ikigadaga amalungu kwa vaanu, apo uwutemi waakwe wiiva waasila.
\v 27 Kusiina umuunu yuna akwiliile kiyinjila mu nanda ya muunu umunya ngufu, kiija amuposhe ifiinu fyakwe nda asimupinyile tangusiina. Leelo pina wámupinya tangusiina umuunu umunya ngufu, baheene akwiliile kimupokha ifiinu fyakwe.”
\p
\v 28 Wájovile, “Shiyooli nikivajovela, avaanu nda vave vitofola avayaanave na kigaha uwunansi uwunji, uNguluvi akhavasaajila uwunansi waanave woona.
\v 29 Leelo umuunu yuna ikimutofola uNumbula uMunofu, uyo uNguluvi asikhamusaajila shiluta, umuunu uyo iiva ana mukhole gwa wunansi uwo wa shiluta.”
\v 30 UYeesu wájovile ndeeno, kiiva avamanyisaaji vala vajovile ana lilungu.
\s Unyina na valukholo lwakwe va Yeesu
\r (Mataayo 12:46-50; Luuka 8:19-21)
\p
\v 31 Baheene umaayi wa Yeesu na valukholo lwakwe vafishile pa nanda yina wáali akwali uYeesu. Vayiima panja, baheene vamufilikha umuunu yumonga mukhati amushemeele uYeesu.
\v 32 Ishipuga sha vaanu vina vamupiliime vamujovela uYeesu kiija, “Umaayi waakho na valukholo lwakho vali panja vikikusakula.”
\p
\v 33 UYeesu wáganile kipulikha wávajovela, “Umaayi wangu na valukholo lwangu vava naani?”
\v 34 Apo wávaloleelile avaanu vina vaali vamupiliime nkholeela, wáaja, “Loleeli, ava vaveene vamaayi vangu na valukholo lwangu!
\v 35 Kiiva umuunu yoyoona yuna isenga gina idobokha uNguluvi, uyo yumwene lukholo lwangu, wulumbu wangu, khanji yu maayi wangu.”
\c 4
\s Ishihwano isha munyansa mbeyu
\r (Mataayo 13:1-9; Luuka 8:4-8)
\p
\v 1 UYeesu wáyansiise kivamanyisa avaanu khanji palubali pa lilamba ilikhome. Ishipuga shikhome sha vaanu shamupiliime na kimuminyiilisa, baheene wáhanjile wáhuluta mu shipugo wáakhala. Avaanu vakheele kunja ku nyi inyuumu.
\v 2 Wávawulaniise amaswi minshi kwa fihwano, na mu mamanyiso gaakwe wájovile,
\v 3 “Mupulisaaje! Umulimaaji yumonga, wálutile kinyansa imbeyu.
\v 4 Pina wáali inyansaga imbeyu, isinji sagwiliile pa nsila, inyuni sayinsa sayilya.
\v 5 Isinji sagwiliile pa shivakwe, pina pasaali ni lilongo linshi, saamela nyangu nyangu kiiva ililongo lyali lisheefu.
\v 6 Pina samelile ilijuva lyanyaanyile, kiiva indela sisafishile pansi, lulwene sayuumile.
\v 7 Isinji sagwiliile mu mapishi ga mimfwa, pina samelile saminyilisiiwe na mimfwa, lulwene sagombwele kikhoma imbumbulu.
\v 8 Na imbeyu isinji sagwiliile pa lilongo ilinofu, saamela na kikula wunofu. Imbeyu simonga sakhomile imbumbulu mashumi gatatu, isinji mashumi mutanda, nasi sinji ligana.”
\v 9 Baheene uYeesu wájeele, “Umuunu yoyoona umunya makutu, apulishe!”
\s UYeesu iganula ishihwano sha munyansa mbeyu
\r (Mataayo 13:10-23; Luuka 8:9-15)
\p
\v 10 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vawuushile pa shipuga sha vaanu, lumo na vanji vina vakhandi vikimufwata, vaaluta palubali. Ukho vayansiise kimuposa vaaja, “Ifihwano ifi uluganulo lwakwe shishi?”
\v 11 UYeesu wávajovile, “Omwe mupeliilwe kimanya imbuusa iya Wutwa wa Nguluvi. Leelo avanji, vijovelwa imola soona kwa fihwano,
\v 12 kiija,
\q ‘Valoleele mandu gina nikigasenga, leelo vasikhagaagaga.
\q Vikigapulikha mandu gina nilogola, leelo vasikhagamanyaga.
\q Yaali yive ndeeno, ndi valambiisila kwa Nguluvi, woope ndi wávasaajila.’\f + \fr 4:12 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Isaaya 6:9-10.\f*”
\p
\v 13 UYeesu wáposiise, “Omwe nda musiimanya ifihwano ifi, musifimanye wuli ifihwano ifinji?
\v 14 Umulimaaji inyansa iLiswi lya Nguluvi.
\v 15 Imbeyu sina sagwiliile mu nsila, sihwananisiwa na vaanu vina vipulikha iLiswi ilyo, baaho uShetaani iyinsa ikiliwuusa iLiswi mu numbula saanave.
\v 16 Imbeyu sina sagwiliile pa shivakwe, sihwananisiwa na vaanu vina vipulikha iLiswi, baaho vikiliposheela kwa wushendeefu.
\v 17 Leelo vasikiliviikha mu numbula. Nda valafisiwe kwa kiiva ya Liswi lya Nguluvi, baaho vikililekha ilihuuvi.
\v 18 Imbeyu sina sagwiliile pa mimfwa, sihwananisiwa na vaanu vina vipulikha iLiswi lya Nguluvi.
\v 19 Leelo paanyuma mu wiikhasi waanave, umuninu, uwusi, nu wupafu wa kiyishendeefya mu fiinu fya mu nyi, fikivaminyiilisa. Ilyo likivagaha vapootwe kikhoma amakhomo.
\v 20 Imbeyu sina sagwiliile pa lilongo ilinofu, sihwananisiwa na vaanu vina vipulikha iLiswi na kiliyanushila. Awo vaveene viikhoma amakhomo, vamonga mashumi gatatu, avanji mashumi mutanda nava vanji ligana limo.”
\s UYeesu iwulanisa kiyinatila iLiswi lya Nguluvi
\r (Luuka 8:16-18)
\p
\v 21 UYeesu wávaposiise avaanu wáaja, “Wuli, avaanu vikunga ulumuli na kigubikha ni shigaana, awu viviikha mu lifungu? Ndaali! Viviikha pa liwumbila.
\v 22 Shilushwali, shoshoona shina shifihiilwe shikhafumbulwa, khanji imbuusa yoyoona yikhamanyikha na kiwonekha, shiyooli fikhava bahawuvalafu.
\v 23 Umuunu yoyoona umunya makutu, apulishe!”
\v 24 Wávajova khanji, “Mukhataje iliswi lina mupulikha. Ishijelo shina mukivajelela avanji, shiisho na yuumwe shina uNguluvi akhavajelela.
\v 25 Kiiva umuunu yoyoona yuna iimanya gina nilogola, uNguluvi asimupeele kimanya mandu. Leelo umuunu yoyoona yuna asikigamanya gina nilogola, hata uwumanyi uwudoodo wuna anawo, akhapokhwa.”
\s UWutwa wa Nguluvi ngaja mbeyu sina siimela
\p
\v 26 UYeesu wájovile kiija, “UWutwa wa Nguluvi ngaja ndeeni, umuunu yumonga wáatile kinyansa imbeyu mu mugunda.
\v 27 Wáali isengaga insengo paminsi, paashilo wáali igonaga, uluhaavi ulo imbeyu siimela na kikula. Umwene asikhasimanyile kiija siikula wuli.
\v 28 Ililongo lilyene lilemfya ifimelo. Taali lilembula ilihamba iliteshe, baheene amahoojo na kuwudugo imbumbulu.
\v 29 Imbumbulu pina sayeela, umuunu uyo iyansa kihenga ni lihenjelo, kiiva uluhaavi lwa nkungulo lwafikha.”
\s UWutwa wa Nguluvi ngaja mbeyu ya mujombe
\r (Mataayo 13:31-32, 34; Luuka 13:18-19)
\p
\v 30 UYeesu wávajovela ishihwano ishinji wáajova, “UWutwa wa Nguluvi niwuhwananise ni shi?
\v 31 UWutwa wa Nguluvi wuhwaneene ni mbeyu iya mujombe. Kiiva imbeyu iyi nangʼana kishila soona mu nyi,
\v 32 leelo nda yivyalwe, yiimela na kiiva shimelo shikhome kishila ifimelo fyona ifya mu mugunda. Amansamba gaakwe giiva makhome, inyuni sikwiliile kisenga ifiwanso fyanave muumo.”
\p
\v 33 UYeesu wáali apimanyisaaga avaanu kwa fihwano ifinji finshi ngaja ifyo. Akhavamanyiise shina vakhandi vakwiliile kimanya.
\v 34 Asikhalogwele na woope shoshoona mbakha fihwano, leelo pina akhandi na vamanyisiwa vaakwe veene duguli, wávaganulilaga soona.
\s UYeesu ivatamya ilipepo ilikhome na mavingu
\r (Mataayo 8:23-27; Luuka 8:22-25)
\p
\v 35 Ilisiku lila pashaamihe, uYeesu wávajoveele avamanyisiwa vaakwe wájeele, “Tilowoshe ku mwambwa yila iya lilamba ilikhome ilya Galilaya.”
\v 36 Baheene, vashileshile ishipuga sha vaanu baaho. Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vayinjiile mu shipugo, muna wáali akwali uYeesu. Khanji avaanu avanji vayangeele ifipugo ifinji valongoseenie nawo.
\v 37 Ishimfulumbwe ishikhali shayansiise kikutukha, amavingu gayansiise kitova ishipugo. Amalenga gayansa kimema mu shipugo.
\v 38 Uluhaavi ulo uYeesu wáali uluvala lwa kunyuma mu shipugo, wáali agonile utulo pashaanya pa lihagulo. Baheene avamanyisiwa vaakwe vamulamwise, vamujovile kiija, “Mumanyisaaji, wuli, usikitusungupila kiija ose tiifwa?”
\p
\v 39 UYeesu wálamukha, wálikhajila ilipepo na kigajova amavingu wáaja, “Vatama! Singamala!” Baaho kwavatama kwava tototo.
\v 40 Wávaposa avamanyisiwa vaakwe wáaja, “Kwashi mutiila? Mushaanali mungaya lihuuvi?”
\v 41 Woope vatiila mandu, vaposania vaajova, “Uyu yu naani, yuna hata ilipepo na mavingu fyona fikimutiila?”
\c 5
\s UYeesu iiponia umunya malungu
\r (Mataayo 8:28-34; Luuka 8:26-39)
\p
\v 1 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vafishile ku mwambwa ya lilamba ilikhome ilya Galilaya, ku nyi ya Vagelaasi.
\v 2 UYeesu wáganile kiyiikha mu shipugo, baaho wámwajile umuunu yumonga yuna ahumile ku majooja. Umuunu uyo akhandi na malungu
\v 3 na ikhalaga mu majooja. Kukhali kusiina muunu yuna wáali akwiliile kimupinya hata na manyololo.
\v 4 Avaanu vakhandi vikimupinya wiila wiila na manyololo ni pingo, leelo wáali idumulaga amanyololo na kidenyanga ipingo. Asaali akwali umuunu umunya ngufu yuna akwiliile kimumena.
\v 5 Insiku soona, paashilo na paminsi wáali ijendaga jendaga mu majooja na mu fidunda. Ukho wáali ilyovanjikha na kiyitemanga temanga na mangʼanga.
\p
\v 6 Wáganile kimwaga uYeesu kwa kutali, wámusijiile pa magulu na kimufugamila.
\v 7 Wákhoosa ishawuti wáaja, “Wee Yeesu, Lusawo lwa Nguluvi uMukhome, wisakula shi kunyangu? Nikikulomba kwa litaawa lya Nguluvi usikhanilafyaga!”
\v 8 Wálogwele ndeeno, kwa kiiva uYeesu akhandi amujovile kiija, “Lilungu muhuma umuunu uyu.”
\p
\v 9 UYeesu wámuposa wáaja, “Ilitaawa lyakho yuuwe naani?” Wámugomosesa wáaja, “Ilitaawa lyangu yuune Legiyoni,\f + \fr 5:9 \fq Legiyoni: \ft Ili litaawa lya Shiluumi. Mu wutwa wa Shiluumi ishipuga sha vasulukhali magana mashumi mutanda (6,000) shitambulwa Legiyoni.\f* kwa kiiva tili vinshi.”
\v 10 Baheene gamulomba uYeesu kiija, asikhagadagaga mu nyi yila.
\p
\v 11 Pala pakhandi pana shidiimilo shikhome sha ngubi, sina sikhandi siilya palubali ya shidunda.
\v 12 Baheene amalungu gamubembelesa gaajova, “Tilomba ututawule tiyinjile mu ngubi sila.”
\v 13 UYeesu wágatawiile amalungu gala, baheene gamuhuma umuunu yula gayinjila mu ngubi sila. Baheene ingubi magana mashumi gavili (2,000) ndeeni, sayiikha luvilo ku munjeema, sagwila mu lilamba ilikhome na kiifwa.
\p
\v 14 Avadimaaji va ngubi sila vaganaga kigaaga ago, vaasiga luvilo kiyalaalisa imola mu lijumbi na mu njinji. Baheene avaanu valutile kiyibedela vaveene gina gasenjekhaga.
\v 15 Vaganaga kifikha pina akhandi akwali uYeesu, vamwaga yula yuna wáali ana malungu akheele pansi, afwalile amenda, khanji ana luhala loona. Baheene avaanu awo vatiilile mandu.
\v 16 Avaanu vala vina vakhagabedeele gina gasenjekhaga, vavataviliilaga avanji shina uYeesu wágadagaga amalungu ni mola sa ngubi.
\v 17 Baheene avakhaaya vala, vayansa kimulomba uYeesu kiija awuushe mu nyi yaanave.
\p
\v 18 UYeesu pina akhandi iyinjila mu shipugo, umuunu yuna wáhumisiwaagwa amalungu wámulomba uYeesu kiija, amuyiitishe valutaniaje lumo.
\v 19 Leelo uYeesu wámukhaanile wáaja, “Wuyaga kunyeenyu, uvajovele amaswi amakhome gina uMutwa wákugahila na kikusungupila.”
\v 20 Baheene umuunu yula wáwuukha, wáyansa kiyalaalisa mu booma ya Dekapoli\f + \fr 5:20 \fq Dekapoli: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, ikhaaya sili ishumi.\f* amaswi goona amakhome gina uYeesu wámugahila. Avaanu woona vaswiga.
\s UYeesu ikimuponia uwashimaayi
\r (Mataayo 9:18-26; Luuka 8:40-56)
\p
\v 21 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe valowokha khanji ni shipugo imwambwa yila iya lilamba ilikhome. Ishipuga ishikhome sha vaanu shamuwunganiliile, bahala palubali lwa lilamba ilyo.
\v 22 Baaho wámuyinsiile uYeesu umuyimililaaji yumonga uwa nanda iya kifuunyila, yuna akhandi itambulwa Yayilo. Wáganile kimwaga, wáfugama pamwandi yaakwe.
\v 23 Wálambiisila wáaja, “Umwali wangu umunangʼana mutamu mandu, ali nkholeela kiifwa. Nilambiisila, shokho umuviishile amawokho gaakho umuponie.”
\v 24 UYeesu wáwuukha lumo nu Yayilo. Avaanu vinshi vamufwatile, vaali vikimuminyiilisa uYeesu.
\p
\v 25 Mu shipuga shishila akhandi akwali uwashimaayi yumonga, yuna akhandi nu wutamu wa kihuma idanda maakha ishumi na gavili.
\v 26 Uwashimaayi uyo wálavile mandu kiluta ku vawusi vinshi. Khanji wámalile uwusi waakwe woona kivahomba avawusi, leelo asikhaponile hata padoodo.
\v 27-28 Uwashimaayi yula wáganile kipulikha imola sa Yeesu, kiija iiponia avaanu, wáhiivile wáaja, “Nda nipyase umutote gwakwe hela, nisiipone.” Baheene wáyansa kishila kwa kiyiminyiilisa mu shipuga sha vaanu, mbakha wáafikha wápyasa umutote gwa Yeesu.
\v 29 Wáganile kipyasa hela umutote gwa Yeesu, baaho idanda yaalekha kihuma, wáamanya kiija wáapona.
\p
\v 30 Uluhaavi luulo, uYeesu wáweene kiija ingufu nsheefu isa kiponesa saahuma. Wáshisetushiile ishipuga sha vaanu wáaposa, “Yu naani yuna wánipyasa umutote gwangu?”
\v 31 Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vamugomosesa vaajova, “Ukivaaga avaanu vakuminyiliise, kwashi wiiposa wiija yu naani wákupyasa?”
\v 32 Leelo uYeesu wáyiteneeshe kiloleela imbali soona, baheene amwaje umuunu yuna wápyasa umutote gwakwe.
\v 33 Baheene uwashimaayi uyo wátungumala na kitetema,\f + \fr 5:33 \fq Kitetema: \ft Akhandi itiila kiiva umuunu umunya wutamu wa kihuma idanda akhandi mwafu, asikhandi iyiitikhwa kimupyasa hata kihansinkhana na vanji. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Njowo sa Valaawi 15:25-33.\f* kwa kiiva wámanyaga gina gasenjekhaga kwa mwene. Wáfugama pamwandi ya Yeesu, wámutaviilila ishiyooli shoona.
\v 34 UYeesu wámujovela wáaja, “Mwali wangu, wahuviilila, lulwene waapona. Ulutaje kwa wulindamafu, waapona khabisa uwutamu waakho.”
\s UYeesu ikimufyusa umwali wa Yayilo
\p
\v 35 UYeesu pina wáali apilogola, avaanu vafishile kihuma ku nanda ya Yayilo, umuyimililaaji wa nanda iya kifuunyila. Vamujoveele uYayilo kiija, “Lekha kimulafya uMumanyisaaji kwa kiiva umwali waakho, wáafwa.”
\v 36 Leelo uYeesu wáganaga kipulikha imola iso, wámujovela uYayilo wáaja, “Usikhatiilaga, nihuvililaga hela.”
\v 37 UYeesu wávakhaana avanji kilongosania lumo nawo, leelo wávatoola uPetulo, Yaakobo nu Yohana ulukholo lwakwe wa Yaakobo.
\p
\v 38 Vaatile kukhaaya kwa yula umuyimililaaji wa nanda iya kifuunyila, uYeesu wávaajile avaanu vamemile vikhoola kwa shawuti nkhome mandu.
\v 39 UYeesu wáyinjila mu nanda, wáaja, “Kwashi musugumiilwe na kikhoola mandu? Umuhinja uyu asifwile, leelo agonile tulo hela.”
\v 40 Avaanu vamuheshile mandu kwa kimusala. Baheene uYeesu wávajova avaanu woona vahume kunja. Wávatoola avasafi va muhinja yula na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vatatu, vayinjila mukhati muna vakhandi vagugoniise umufimba.
\v 41 Wámukhata iliwokho wámujova, “\tl Talita kumi,\tl*” uluganulo lwakwe, “Owe muhinja, nikikujova yiima!”
\v 42 Baaho umuhinja yula wáyiima, wáyansa kijenda. Wáali ana maakha ishumi na gavili. Avaanu vaswiga mandu.
\v 43 UYeesu wávakhaana mandu kiija, vasikhamujovelaga umuunu yoyoona imola iso. Baheene wávajovela avasafi va muhinja uyo kiija, vamupeele ishakiilya.
\c 6
\s UYeesu ikhaanwa ku Nasaleti
\r (Mataayo 13:53-58; Luuka 4:16-30)
\p
\v 1 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vawuushile lumo, valutile ku lijumbi ilya Yeesu ilya ku Nasaleti.
\v 2 Pina lyafishile ilijuva lya Sabaato, wáyansiise kimanyisa mu nanda iya kifuunyila. Avaanu vinshi vina vamupuliishe, vaswijile mandu amamanyiso gaakwe. Vaposeenie vaveene kiija, “Khaa! Wágaaga kwi amaswi aga? Ulumanyo ulu apeliilwe nu naani? Khanji wásaaga kwi ingufu isa kisenjela amabikha aga?
\v 3 Wuli, uyu asili yuyula umuhongolaaji, ulusawo lwa Maliya, na vanangʼana vaakwe uYaakobo, uYoose, uYuuda nu Simoni? Avawulumbu vaakwe vasili vaveene tiikhala lumo baaha panyeesu?” Baheene vakhaana kimuhuviilila.
\p
\v 4 UYeesu wávajoveele wáaja, “Umukuwamalago itiilwa shila luvala, leelo ku nyi yaakwe, na ku valukholo lwakwe, na kukhaaya yaakwe asitiilwa.”
\v 5 Asawuyile asenje amabikha minshi ukho, leelo wávavishiile amawokho avatamu vasheefu, woope vaponile.
\v 6 Wáswijile mandu kiiva avaanu avanji vasamuhuviliile. Baheene uYeesu wáwuushile wájendile jendile mu majumbi aganji kivamanyisa avaanu.
\s UYeesu ikivafilikha avanandeje vaakwe kikhoma //iLiswi lya Nguluvi
\r (Mataayo 10:5-15; Luuka 9:1-6)
\p
\v 7 UYeesu wávashemeelile avanandeje vaakwe ishumi na vavili, wáyansa kivafilikha vavili vavili, na kivapeela uwutawulilwa uwa kigadaga amalungu.
\v 8 Baheene wávakhanyansiise wáaja, “Nikivatawula musumulaje nkwegu seene, leelo ndaali kisumula ishiinu shoshoona pina mushuula, wala shakiilya, wala mbukuli, wala hela.
\v 9 Nikivatawula mufwalaje indaatu, leelo ndaali kisumula umwenda ugwa kiyanunkhania.”
\v 10 Khanji wávajova wáaja, “Ilitembe lina musiyinjile, mukhalaje muumo mbakha pina muwuukha mu lijumbi ilyo.
\v 11 Khanji pala pina vasikivasaajisa wala kivapuliisa, wuukhaji na kikungʼuuna amankundi gina gali mu nsayo sa magulu geenyu\f + \fr 6:11 \fq Kikungʼuuna amankundi gina gali mu nsayo sa magulu geenyu: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, aVayahuudi vinshi pina viiwuya kunyaanave, vakhandi vikungʼuuna amankundi ga nyi sina sisili sa Vayahuudi mu nsayo sa magulu gaanave, kiiva vakhandi viijova kiija inyi isinji mwikho. Avanandeje va Yeesu vagahaga ndeeno, kivawonensa aVayahuudi vina vasikhaanaga imola sa Nguluvi kiija, uNguluvi ikivaaga vaafu, nda vasilambiisila, akhavahiga.\f* yive shimanyilo sha kihigwa kwa kiyikhaana iMola iNofu.”
\p
\v 12 Baheene avanandeje vaakwe vawuushile viiluta kikhoma kiija, avaanu valambiisile uwunansi waanave.
\v 13 Khanji vadagaga amalungu minshi. Vakhandi vikivasusuuta amafuta avatamu vinshi, woope vakhandi viipona.
\s UYohana uMutwiniaji iibudwa
\r (Mataayo 14:1-12; Luuka 9:7-9)
\p
\v 14 Umutwa uHelode\f + \fr 6:14 \fq UHelode: \ft Uyo asili yula yuna uwiihe wávabudaga avaana uluhaavi luna wásawaagwa uYeesu. Yimba iliswi \fqa Helode \ft mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* wápulikhaga imola sa Yeesu, kiiva ilitaawa lya Yeesu lyapulisikhaga imbali soona. Avaanu avanji vakhandi vapilogola, “UYohana uMutwiniaji wáfyukha kihuma kwa vina vafwile. Lulwene ana ngufu isa kisenga amabikha.”
\v 15 Avanji vaajova, “Yu mukuwamalago uEliya.”\f + \fr 6:15 \ft AVayahuudi vakhandi vahepeleese kiija akhayinsa khanji umukuwamalago uEliya, ayandaale kiyinsa kwa Kilisito. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Malaaki 4:5-6.\f* Avanji vaajova, “Uyu mukuwamalago ngaja yuyuumo na vakuwamalago ava pawukuulu.”
\v 16 Baheene uHelode wáganile kipulikha imola iso, wájovile, “Uyo yumwene uYohana, yuna namudumwile umutwe, wáfyukha!”
\p
\v 17-18 Isi mola sa Helode pina wámubudile uYohana. UHelode wámutoolile uHelodiya umudala wa munangʼana waakwe uFilipo. Baheene uYohana wámujovile uHelode kiija, “Mwikho kimutoola umudala wa munangʼana waakho uFilipo.” Baheene uHelode wáfiliishe avaanu vamukhate uYohana na kimudindila mu shifungo.
\v 19 Baaho uHelodiya wámukhalaliile uYohana na kimutegama kiija amubude, leelo wágombolaga,
\v 20 kiiva uHelode akhandi ikimudiima uYohana. Wámutiilaga uYohana kiiva uYohana akhandi mugolofu, akhandi munya numbula nofu. UHelode wálunduveele mandu pina akhandi ikimupuliisa uYohana, leelo akhandi apidobokha amupulisaaje.
\p
\v 21 Baheene uHelodiya wápatile imwenshe iya kimubuda uYohana. Ilisiku limonga uHelode wáali ni shiwungo isha kikumbukha kisawa kwa mwene. Wátelekhaga ishakiilya ishinofu, baheene wávashemeela avavaha vaakwe va livansa, avakhome va vayimililaaji va vasulukhali na vina vakhandi vilongosa mu nyi ya Galilaya.
\v 22 Baheene wáyinjiile umwali wa Helodiya, wáneenile, wávashendefiise uHelode na vahensa vina vaali mula. Baheene umutwa uHelode wámujovile umuhinja yula wáaja, “Lomba ishiinu shoshoona shina wisakula, na yuune nisikupeele.”
\v 23 Khanji wáyiyijile wáaja, “Shoshoona shina hambi ukinilomba nisikupeele, hata wuve uwutwa wangu hambi niigava paakhati ulubali lumonga nisikupeele.”
\p
\v 24 Umwali yula wálutile kimuposa umaayi waakwe kiija, “Nilombe shishi?” Umaayi waakwe wáaja, “Lomba umutwe gwa Yohana uMutwiniaji.”
\v 25 Umuhinja yula wátinile nyangu nyangu kwa mutwa uHelode wálomba wáaja, “Nilomba umutwe gwa Yohana uMutwiniaji mu siniya.”
\p
\v 26 Umutwa uHelode wáganile kipulikha ago, wásugumilwagwa mandu. Leelo kiiva akhandi ayiyiijile pa vahensa woona vala, wágombwele kikhaana amalombo gaakwe.
\v 27 Baaho umutwa uHelode wámufilikha umusulukhali aleete umutwe gwa Yohana. Umusulukhali wálutile mu shifungo, wámudumula uYohana umutwe.
\v 28 Wáviikha umutwe gula mu siniya, wámupeela umuhinja yula, woope wámupeela umaayi waakwe.
\v 29 Avamanyisiwa va Yohana uMutwiniaji, vaganile kipulikha imola iyo, valutile kigutoola umufimba na kigusiila mu lijooja.
\s UYeesu ikivaliisa avaanu magana mashumi gasaanu (5,000)
\r (Mataayo 14:13-21; Luuka 9:10-17; Yohana 6:1-14)
\p
\v 30 Vala avanandeje vatinile kwa Yeesu, vamutavililaga goona gina vagahaga na gina vamanyiise.
\v 31 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe, vakunyaga na kiiva nu luhaavi ulwa kiilya, kiiva avaanu vinshi vakhandi vipyanisania kiyinsa kwa Yeesu. Baheene uYeesu wávajova avamanyisiwa vaakwe wáaja, “Tilute apanji palubali tikhale tituuye padoodo.”
\v 32 Baheene vayinjiile mu shipugo, viiluta palubali pina pangaya vaanu.
\p
\v 33 Leelo avaanu vinshi vavaajile pina viwuukha, vamanyaga kuna viiluta. Avaanu kihuma mu makhaaya goona valutile luvilo valongola kifikha.
\v 34 UYeesu wáganile kiyiikha mu shipugo, wáshaajile ishipuga shikhome sha vaanu. Wávasungupilaga kwa kiiva vakhandi ngaja nkholo sina singaya mudimaaji. Baheene wáyansa kivawulanisa amaswi minshi.
\p
\v 35 Pashinyiijuva, avamanyisiwa vaakwe valutile kwa Yeesu vamujovela kiija, “Panu tikheele pa lunyikha patali na majumbi, khanji yiveele shaamihe.
\v 36 Uvahwese avaanu, valute mu magunda gina gali nkholeela na mu njinji, vayigulilaje ifyakiilya.”
\v 37 Baheene uYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “Omwe muvapeele yuumwe ishakiilya.” Vaaposa kiija, “Wuli! Titoole kwi ihela isa mahombo ga nsiku magana gavili (200),\f + \fr 6:37 \fq Ihela isa mahombo ga nsiku magana gavili (200): \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe, \fqa dinaali magana gavili (200)\fqa*. \f* tilute tigule ishakiilya na tivapeele?”
\v 38 Wávaposiise wáaja, “Muna makhaate galinga? Mulute muloleele.” Vaganaga kimanya vamujovela kiija, “Tina makhaate gasaanu ni nswi sivili.”
\p
\v 39 UYeesu wávalajisa avamanyisiwa vaakwe kiija, vajoveli avaanu woona vakhale fipuga fipuga pa lisole iliigu.
\v 40 Woope vaakhala fipuga fipuga, panu ligana, panu mashumi gasaanu.
\v 41 UYeesu wátoola amakhaate gala gasaanu ni nswi sila sivili wáloleela kushaanya, wámuhonjesa uNguluvi. Wámenyulania amakhaate, wávapeela avamanyisiwa vaakwe, kiija vavagavile avaanu. Inswi sivili sila, soope wávagavila woona.
\v 42 Avaanu woona vaalya, vayikuta.
\v 43 Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vakungaania amamenyulanie ni nswi, fyamema matunduti ishumi na gavili.
\v 44 Avaanu woona vina valiisaga vaali vinshi, avagoosi veene duguli vaali magana mashumi gasaanu (5,000).
\s UYeesu ijenda pashaanya pa malenga
\r (Mataayo 14:22-33; Yohana 6:16-21)
\p
\v 45 Baaho uYeesu wávalajisa avamanyisiwa vaakwe, vayinjile mu shipugo, valongole kiluta ku mwambwa ya lilamba ilikhome ilya Galilaya, ku lijumbi lya Betisayida. Uluhaavi ulo umwene akhandi ikishihwesa ishipuga sha vaanu.
\v 46 Wáganile kimala kivahwesa avaanu, wálutile ku shidunda kifuunya.
\p
\v 47 Pina shikhandi shaamihe, ishipugo shaali paakhati pa lilamba ilikhome, uYeesu wáali mwene duguli kunja ku nyi inyuumu.
\v 48 Wávaajile avamanyisiwa vaakwe vigombola kikholojela ishipugo, kiiva ilipepo likhandi likivatinia kunyuma. Kwali kusinahenje kunena, uYeesu wáyansa kijenda pashaanya pa malenga iiluta ku vamanyisiwa vaakwe, ngaja ishilanisa.
\v 49 Vaganile kimwaga ijenda pashaanya pa malenga vahiivile kiija linguluvi, valyovile ilyowo,
\v 50 kiiva woona vamwagaga vatiilaga mandu. Baaho uYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “Jimfyaji inumbula, yuune, musikhatiilaji!”
\v 51 Baheene woope wáyinjila mu shipugo muna vakhandi vakwali, nali lipepo lyavatama, vaswijile mandu.
\v 52 Vasikhameenye amabikha ga makhaate, kiiva inumbula saanave sikhandi nyuumu.
\s UYeesu iiponia avatamu mu Genesaleti
\r (Mataayo 14:34-36)
\p
\v 53 Vaganile kilowokha mu lilamba ilikhome ilya Galilaya, vafishile mu nyi ya Genesaleti, vayiimya ishipugo pa lilowokho.
\v 54 Vaganile kihuma mu shipugo, baaho avaanu vamanyaga kiija yu Yeesu.
\v 55 Valutile viisiga shila luvala lwa mu nyi yila yoona, vayansa kivatoola avatamu na kivasumula mu lupaasa, na kivatwala kuna vipulikha kiija uYeesu akwali.
\v 56 Shila luvala uYeesu luna akhandi iita, mu njinji indoodo, mu majumbi amavaha, na mu magunda, avaanu vavaviishile avatamu vaanave pa munaada. Vamulombile uYeesu kiija avatawule avatamu vapyase ulupembo lwa mwenda gwakwe hela. Baheene avatamu woona vina vapyasaaga vaponaga.
\c 7
\s UYeesu ikigakhaana amamanyiso aga ngʼoma sa vambuya
\r (Mataayo 15:1-9)
\p
\v 1 Ilisiku limonga, aVafalisaayo na vamanyisaaji vamonga va ndaji sa Musa, vayinsile kihuma ku Yelusalemu. Vamukungaanila uYeesu.
\v 2 Vavaajile avamanyisiwa va Yeesu vamonga viilya ishakiilya na mawokho maafu kiiva vasikhayiyojile.
\v 3 AVafalisaayo na Vayahuudi woona, vakhaniilwe kiilya kuno vasiwuyiliile khanji kiyiyooga wunofu amawokho,\f + \fr 7:3 \fq Kiyiyooga wunofu amawokho: \ft AVafalisaayo vijovaga, umuunu nda apyase ishakiilya asiyiyoojile amawokho na kifuunya tangusiina, ishakiilya isho shiiva shashafukha, ndeeno shikimugaha yuna iilya ave mushaafu. AVafalisaayo vaswigaga, kiiva uYeesu asikhatunile kishafukha kwa vamanyisiwa vaakwe. \f* shina yisakulwa mu ngʼoma ya vambuyaanave.
\v 4 Khanji umuunu nda ahumile ku munaada asiyiitikhwa kiilya kuno asiyivaleese. Gakwali amaswi aganji gina vaposheelaga na kiyinatila gaali aga kiyoosa wunofu inkhonkholo ngaja ikhoomasi, shifugo nafi finji ifya kiliila.
\p
\v 5 Baheene aVafalisaayo na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa vamuposiise uYeesu kiija, “Kwashi avamanyisiwa vaakho vasiyinatila ingʼoma sina avambuyeesu vatuleshelaga, leelo viilya na mawokho maafu?”
\v 6 UYeesu wájovile wáaja, “Muli vamyansi omwe! UIsaaya wálogwele ga shiyooli pina wákuwiilwe amalago kwa kiiva yeenyu. Wáyandiishe kiija,
\q ‘UNguluvi iija,
\q “Avaanu ava vikinitiila kwa kilogola kwene hela,
\q leelo inumbula saanave sisikinihiiva one.
\q
\v 7 Woope vikinifuunya hela one,
\q khanji vimanyisa amamanyiso ga ndaji sa vaanu
\q na kiija ndaji sangu.”\f + \fr 7:6-7 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Isaaya 29:13.\f*’
\m
\v 8 “Omwe musileshile indaji isa Nguluvi, musikheete ingʼoma sa vaanu.”
\p
\v 9 UYeesu wáali apikivajovaga, “Omwe mwidobokha kityega kwa wusugu indaji sa Nguluvi, baheene mupate kikwisa ingʼoma seenyu!
\v 10 UMusa\f + \fr 7:10 \fq UMusa: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Musa \ft mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* wávajoveele kiija, ‘Uvatiilaje uwiiho nu maayi waakho.’\f + \fr 7:10 \xt Kihuma 20:12; Luuju lwa Ndaji 5:16.\f* Khanji wájovile, ‘Yoyoona yuna ikimuliga uwiihe awu umaayi waakwe, uyo wa kibudwa.’\f + \fr 7:10 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Kihuma 21:17; Njowo sa Valaawi 20:9.\f*
\v 11 Leelo omwe mwijova kiija umuunu akwiliile kimujovela uwiihe awu umaayi waakwe kiija, ‘Ifiinu fina naava niija nikutanje owe, naahumya kwa Nguluvi.’
\v 12 Ndeeno, omwe mukimukhamiilisa umuunu aleshe kivatanga uwiihe awu umaayi waakwe.
\v 13 Lulwene mwisala iLiswi lya Nguluvi kiiva ingʼoma sa mamanyiso gina muyanunkhana. Khanji mwisenga amaswi minshi ngaja ago.”
\s Ifiinu fina fikimushafula umuunu
\r (Mataayo 15:10-20)
\p
\v 14 UYeesu wáshemeelile khanji ishipuga sha vaanu wáshijovela wáaja, “Munipulisaaje woona, khanji mugamanyaje gina niijova.
\v 15 Ishiinu shina shikimuyinjila umuunu kihuma kunja, shisikwiliile kimushafula. Leelo shina shiihuma mukhati mu numbula ya muunu, shisheene shikimushafula umuunu. [\v 16 Umuunu umunya makutu ga kipulikha, apulishe.]\f + \fr 7:16 \ft Amaswi aga, gakusiina mu mayandikhwa agamonga amakuulu.\f*”
\p
\v 17 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vashileshile ishipuga, vayinjila mu nanda yimonga. Baheene vamuposiise uluganulo ulwa shihwano shila.
\v 18 UYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “Wuli, na yuumwe mushaanali musiimanya? Wuli, musimeenye kiija ishiinu shina iilya umuunu shisikwiliile kimushafula umuunu?
\v 19 Umuunu pina iilya ishakiilya shisiiluta mu numbula leelo shiiluta mu wutumbu, baheene paanyuma shiihuma kunja.” UYeesu wáganile kilogola ndeeno wáyitiishe kiija ifyakiilya fyona finofu.
\p
\v 20 UYeesu wáyonjelesa wáaja, “Ishiinu shina shiihuma mu numbula, isho shisheene shina shikimushafula umuunu.
\v 21 Kiiva mu numbula ya muunu mumwene muna giihuma amahiiva amavi, uwushemi, uwuhiiji, uwubudaaji,
\v 22 uwaafu uwa kijenda na vadala va kunja, uwushooyo, amaleefi, uwujanjilisaaji, uwiifu, kitofola, uwuhonje nu wuyasu.
\v 23 Uwunansi woona uwu wiihuma mukhati mu numbula ya muunu, gageene gina gikimushafula umuunu.”
\s Ilihuuvi ilya washimaayi yuna asili Muyahuudi
\r (Mataayo 15:21-28)
\p
\v 24 UYeesu wáwuukha pala, wáaluta ku mbali isa Tiilo ni Sidoni. Wáyinjila mu nanda yimonga, akhandi asidobweshe umuunu yoyoona amanye kiija akwali pala, leelo hata ndeeno avaanu vamanyaga.
\v 25 Uwashimaayi yumonga yuna wáali nu mwali umunya lilungu, wápuliishe imola sa Yeesu. Baaho, wáyinsa wáfugama pa Yeesu.
\v 26 Uwashimaayi yula yuna asili Muyahuudi, wahumile ku booma ya Foyinike mu nyi ya Siliya. Wámulomba uYeesu kiija, alidaje ililungu lina lili mwa mwali waakwe.
\p
\v 27 Baheene uYeesu wámujovile wáaja, “Uleshe tangusiina avaana valye vayikute, kiiva lusili lunofu kitoola ishakiilya sha vaana na kisitoosesa imbwa.”\f + \fr 7:27 \fq Vaana: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, \fqa Vayahuudi\fqa*. \fq Imbwa: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, \fqa vina vasili Vayahuudi.\f*
\v 28 Umwene wámuyanshile wáaja, “Shiyooli Mutwa, leelo nasi mbwa sina sili pansi pa meesa siilya fina avaana valageese pansi.”\fig |42_Mark7.28_DogsTable.jpg|col|||Imbwa siilya pansi pa meesa|7:28\fig*
\v 29 UYeesu wámujovile wáaja, “Kiiva iliswi lina wáajova, wuyaga kukhaaya. Ililungu lyamuleshela umwaliwo.”
\v 30 Uwashimaayi yula wáganile kifikha kukhaaya yaakwe, wámwajile umwali agonile pa wusaga, lila ililungu limuhumile.
\s UYeesu ikimuponia umuunu umbwibwi khanji mudinde
\p
\v 31 UYeesu wáwuukha uluvala ulwa ku Tiilo kishilila ku Sidoni, wáfishile ku lilamba ilikhome ilya Galilaya, mu booma ya Dekapoli.\f + \fr 7:31 \fq Dekapoli: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, ikhaaya sili ishumi.\f*
\v 32 Ukho vamuleteele umuunu umbwibwi, khanji mudinde amakutu. Vamulomba uYeesu kiija amuviishile amawokho, amuponie.
\p
\v 33 UYeesu wámubagwile umuunu yula mu shipuga sha vaanu, wáaluta nawo palubali. Wáfuunyila amata indole saakwe, wámupyasa ulumili wáyinjisa indole mu makutu.
\v 34 Baheene wáloleelile kushaanya ku wulanga wátuuya kwa ngufu, wáaja, “\tl Efata!\tl*” Uluganulo lwakwe, “Dindukha!”
\v 35 Baaho amakutu gaakwe gadindukha na ulumili lwahogokha, baheene wáyansa kilogola wunofu.
\p
\v 36 UYeesu wávakhaanile kiija, musikhamujovelaji muunu sina wámusenjela. Pina wáshilile kivakhaana, baheene aveene vashilile kiyalaalisa imola iso ku vaanu woona.
\v 37 Avaanu vaswigaga mandu vaajova, “Insengo sina isenga soona nofu mandu! Umwene avapeelile avadinde kipulikha na vambwibwi vilogola wunofu.”
\c 8
\s UYeesu ikivaliisa avaanu magana mashumi gana (4,000)
\r (Mataayo 15:32-39)
\p
\v 1 Mu nsiku sila, ilisiku ilinji ishipuga shikhome sha vaanu shakungaanile kwa Yeesu. Avaanu vala pina vakhandi vakheele nu Yeesu nsiku sitatu, ishakiilya shaanave shasilaga. Baheene uYeesu wávashemeela avamanyisiwa vaakwe wáajova,
\v 2 “Nikivasungupila avaanu ava, kiiva vakheele noose nsiku sitatu, lino vagaya shakiilya.
\v 3 Nda nivatawule kiija vawuye kukhaaya saanave pina vana njala, vasisilishe mu nsila, khanji avanji viihuma kutali.”
\p
\v 4 Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vamugomosesa vaaja, “Tisigaaje kwi amakhaate pa lunyikha panu aga kivakwila avaanu woona ava?”
\v 5 UYeesu wávaposa wáaja, “Muna makhaate galinga?” Vamugomosesa vaaja, “Gali fungati.”
\v 6 Baheene uYeesu wávalajisa avaanu kiija vakhale pansi. Wátoola amakhaate gala fungati, wámuhonjesa uNguluvi. Wámenyulania, wávapeela avamanyisiwa vaakwe, woope vavagavila avaanu woona.
\v 7 Khanji vakhandi nu tuswi tusheefu. UYeesu wáhonjesa, wávajova avamanyisiwa vaakwe kiija, soope vavagavile avaanu.
\v 8 Avaanu valiisaga, vayikuta. Baheene avamanyisiwa vakunganiaga amakhaate amamenyulanie gina gasigalaga, gamemile matunduti fungati.
\v 9 Avaanu vina valiisaga ishakiilya shila, vakhandi ngaja magana mashumi gana (4,000).
\v 10 Baaho uYeesu wávahwesa, wáyangala mu shipugo lumo na vamanyisiwa vaakwe, wáaluta ku mbali isa ku Dalimanuta.
\s AVafalisaayo visakula uYeesu agahe amabikha
\r (Mataayo 12:38-42; 16:1-4)
\p
\v 11 AVafalisaayo valutile kwa Yeesu, vayansa kikhaanania na woope. Vakhandi vikimujela vikimusakula avawonense ishimanyilo, kiwonensa kiija afiliikhwe nu Nguluvi.
\v 12 UYeesu wásugumilwa mu numbula, wáaja, “Ishisafi ishi shisakula ishimanyilo, shiyooli nikivajovela musikhashaaga shimanyilo shoshoona.”
\v 13 Wávalekha, wáyinjila khanji mu shipugo valowokha mu lilamba ilikhome vaaluta ku mwambwa yinji.
\s UYeesu ipavila ulwa lihelu lya Vafalisaayo nu //mutwa uHelode
\r (Mataayo 16:5-12)
\p
\v 14 Pina vakhandi vilowokha, vakhandi vana mukhaate gumo mu shipugo, kwa kiiva avamanyisiwa vaakwe vakhandi vasamiilwe kitoola amakhaate.
\v 15 UYeesu wávasimila wáaja, “Nikivajovela kiija muyivavalaje ni lihelu\f + \fr 8:15 \fq Lihelu: \ft Shiinu sha kiwumulila amakhaate. Mu lukhalala ulu, iliswi ilyo uluganulo lwakwe, imola imbi sa Vafalisaayo nu Helode sina siyambuhisa ku vaanu vanji. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Mataayo 16:6-12.\f* ilya Vafalisaayo ni lihelu ilya mutwa uHelode.”
\v 16 Avamanyisiwa vala vayansa kijovelana veene viija, “Ilogola ndeeno kwa kiiva tisatoola amakhaate.”
\p
\v 17 UYeesu wáamanya gala gina viijova, wáaja, “Kwashi mwikhaanania yuumwe kiija mungaya makhaate? Mushaanali musinakumbushe na kimanya? Inumbula seenyu nyuumu?
\v 18 Muna meeho, leelo kwashi musiloleela? Khanji muna makutu, leelo kwashi musipulikha? Musikumbukha,
\v 19 uluhaavi lula luna namenyulaga amakhaate gasaanu, valiisaga vaanu magana mashumi gasaanu (5,000), mwakunganiaga matunduti galinga gina vasigasaaga?” Vaaja, “Matunduti lishumi na gavili.”
\p
\v 20 “Pina nimenyulaga amakhaate fungati, valiisaga vaanu magana mashumi gana (4,000), mwakunganiaga amasigase matunduti galinga?” Vaaja, “Takunganiaga matunduti fungati.”
\v 21 Wávaposiise wáaja, “Wuli, mushaanali musinaamanye?”
\s UYeesu ikimuponia umupofu ku Betisayida
\p
\v 22 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vafishile ku Betisayida. Kula avaanu vamutwaliile umupofu yumonga, vamulombile amupyase, ulugulumilo lwanave apone.
\v 23 UYeesu wámukhata iliwokho umupofu yula, wáhumile nawo mu lujinji lula. Wámufuunyila amata ku meeho, baheene wámuviishila amawokho, wámuposa wáaja, “Ukishaaga shimonga?”
\v 24 Umupofu yula wáloleelile, wáaja, “Nikivaaga avaanu vijenda, leelo viwonekha ngaja mapishi.”
\p
\v 25 UYeesu wáwuyansaaga khanji, wáviikha amawokho gaakwe ku meeho ga mupofu. Apo umupofu yula wákhangasa kiloleela. Ameeho gaakwe gaponaga, wáloleelaga wunofu ifiinu fyona.
\v 26 UYeesu wámutawulaga awuyaje kukhaaya, wáajova, “Pina wiiwuya usikhashililaga mu lijumbi.”
\s UPetulo ikimubedela uYeesu kiija Mukulusaaji
\r (Mataayo 16:13-20; Luuka 9:18-21)
\p
\v 27 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe, vawuushile vayansa kiluta ku booma ya Kayisaliya-Filipi. Pina vakhandi mu nsila wávaposa wáajova, “Avaanu viija one yuune naani?”
\v 28 Vamugomosesa vaaja, “Vamonga viija yuuwe Yohana Mutwiniaji, avanji viija yuuwe Eliya mukuwamalago, avanji viija mukuwamalago ngaja vakuwamalago ava paanyuma.”
\v 29 Wávaposiise wáaja, “Omwe mwijova one yuune naani?” UPetulo wámugomosesa wáaja, “Owe yuuwe Mukulusaaji yuna uNguluvi wátahisaaga kimufilikha.”\f + \fr 8:29 \fq Mukulusaaji yuna uNguluvi wátahisaaga kimufilikha: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. Kwa Shihebulaniya viija \fqa Mesiya\fqa*. AVayahuudi vatambulaga ilitaawa lya Mesiya kiija, yu muunu yuna wábagulwagwa nu Nguluvi. Khanji wátahisiwaagwa kifilikhwa kiiva Mukulusaaji kwa vaanu. Yimba iliswi \fqa Kilisito\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f*
\v 30 UYeesu wávakhaana vasikhamujovelaga muunu yoyoona kiija, umwene Mukulusaaji.\f + \fr 8:30 \fq Mukulusaaji: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. \f*
\s UYeesu itaviilila shina hambi iifwa na kifyukha
\r (Mataayo 16:21-28; Luuka 9:22-27)
\p
\v 31 UYeesu wáyansiise kivawulanisa avamanyisiwa vaakwe kiija, umwene Lusawo lwa Muunu, isakulwa kiiva na malava minshi na kikhaanwa na vakhome va Vayahuudi, avatambule avakhome na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa. Akhabudwa, leelo ilisiku lya wutatu akhafyukha.
\v 32 UYeesu wájovaga amaswi ago bila kifiha. UPetulo wámutoolaga uYeesu wáaluta na woope palubali, wáyansa kimukhajila kiija, asikhalogolaga amaswi ngaja ago.
\v 33 Leelo uYeesu wásetukhaga, wávaloleela avamanyisiwa vaakwe, wámukhajila uPetulo wáaja, “Wuukha kumwandi yangu owe Shetaani, kiiva amahiiva gaakho gasili ga Nguluvi, leelo wihiiva ga vaanu.”
\p
\v 34 Baheene uYeesu wáshishemeela ishipuga sha vaanu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe, wávajovela wáaja, “Umuunu yoyoona nda isakula kinifwata one, aleshe gina agadobweshe, ayihumye anifwate hata nda yive kiifwa.\f + \fr 8:34 \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe, \fqa Umuunu yoyoona yuna isakula kinifwata ayikhaanaje yumwene, asumule umusalaaba gwakwe na kinifwata wiila.\f*
\v 35 Kiiva, umuunu yoyoona yuna isakula kiwusaajila uwuumi waakwe, uyo akhawuyasa. Leelo umuunu yuna ikiwuyasa uwuumi waakwe kwa kiiva ya one na kwa kiiva ya Mola iNofu, uyo asiwupate uwuumi wa shiluta.
\v 36 Poona umuunu akhayambulila shishi, kipata uwusi woona wa nyi na kiwuyasa uwuumi wa shiluta?
\v 37 Lino, umuunu ahumye shishi kipyanisa uwuumi waakwe? Kusiina shiinu shoshoona.
\v 38 Umuunu yoyoona yuna ikiniwonela nsoni one na mamanyiso gangu mu vaanu va shisafi ishi, vina viigaha uwushemi nu wunansi uwunji, na yuune yuna nili Lusawo lwa Muunu, pina nikhava niyinsa mu wutupikho wa Daada lumo na vamalayikha vaakwe, nikhamuwonela nsoni umuunu uyo.”
\c 9
\nb
\v 1 UYeesu wáyonjelesa kijova wáaja, “Shiyooli nikivajovela kiija, avamonga vina vakwali panu vasikhafwa mbakha pina vakhawaaga uWutwa wa Nguluvi wuyinsa kwa ngufu.”
\s UYeesu ihambukha umuvili
\r (Mataayo 17:1-13; Luuka 9:28-36)
\p
\v 2 Saganile kishila nsiku mutanda, uYeesu wávatoolile uPetulo, uYaakobo nu Yohana. Wálutile nawo ku shidunda ishitali mandu, ukho vakhandi veene. Baheene pina vali pala, uYeesu wáhambukha umuvili gwakwe paveene,
\v 3 amenda gaakwe gaava mavalafu gingʼaala mandu, na kusiina umukhansaaji wa menda panja panu yuna akwiliile kigavalasa ngaja amenda ga Yeesu.
\p
\v 4 Baheene vatwiwukha avakuwamalago uEliya nu Musa,\f + \fr 9:4 \fq UEliya nu Musa: \ft Awo vakhandi vakuwamalago avakhome. UMusa wávalongosaaga aVaisilaheli kihuma ku Misili, kiluta ku nyi ya Isilaheli. UEliya akhandi ihuviililwa kiija, akhatina mu nyi pina asinayinse uMesiya.\f* vaava vilogola nu Yeesu.
\v 5 UPetulo wámujovela uYeesu wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji, lunofu ose tive tiikhala bahanu. Lino tisenje ingono sitatu. Yimo yive yaakho, yimonga ya Musa, iyinji yive ya Eliya.”
\v 6 UPetulo asikhamanyile iijova shishi, kiiva umwene na vayine vaali viswigaga.
\p
\v 7 Baheene lyayinsile ilifunde, lyavagubikha, ishawuti yapuliisikha kihuma mu lifunde yina yiijova, “Uyu yumwene Lusawo lwangu. Nimuganile, mumupulisaaje!”
\v 8 Baaho vaganile kiloleela kuno na kuno vasamwajile umuunu uyunji, leelo vamwajile uYeesu mwene duguli.
\p
\v 9 Pina vakhandi viyiikha kihuma ku shidunda, uYeesu wávakhaana kiija, “Musikhamujovelaji umuunu yoyoona gina mwagaaga kuno, mbakha uluhaavi luna uLusawo lwa Muunu, akhafyukha kihuma kwa vina vafwile.”
\v 10 Na vaveene vayinatilaga iliswi lina wájovile uYeesu, kuno vapiposania veene kwa veene kiija, “Kihuma mu mfwa lulwene luganulo lushi?”
\p
\v 11 Vamuposa, uYeesu vaaja, “Kwashi avamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa viija mbakha ayinse tangusiina uEliya, baheene kuunyuma uKilisito?”\f + \fr 9:11 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Malaaki 4:5-6.\f*
\v 12 UYeesu wáajova wáaja, “Shiyooli, uEliya asilongole tangusiina, kinosa injowo soona. Khanji, kwashi yiyandiikhwe mu Mayandikhwa aManofu kiija, uLusawo lwa Muunu akhalafisiwa mandu na kisalwa?
\v 13 Leelo nikivajovela kiija, uEliya shi wáyinsaga,\f + \fr 9:13 \fq UEliya shi wáyinsaga: \ft UYeesu ikimulogola uYohana uMutwiniaji, yuna insengo saakwe sikhandi sihwaneene nu Eliya.\f* vamugahilaga fivi ngaja shina yiyandiikhwe ulwa mwene mu Mayandikhwa aManofu.”
\s UYeesu ikimuponia umudiimi umunya lilungu
\r (Mataayo 17:14-21; Luuka 9:37-43)
\p
\v 14 UYeesu, uPetulo, uYaakobo nu Yohana vafishile uluvala luna vakhandi vakwali avamanyisiwa vala avanji. Vashaajile ishipuga ishikhome sha vaanu baaho. Avamanyisaaji avamonga va ndaji sa Musa vaali vikhananiaga na vamanyisiwa va Yeesu.
\v 15 Avaanu vala pina vamwajile uYeesu vaswijile mandu, vamulutiile luvilo, vamuhunjila.
\v 16 UYeesu wávaposiise wáaja, “Shiinu shishi shina mukhaanania?”
\p
\v 17 Umuunu yumonga mukhati mu shipuga shila, wámuyanshile wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji, naava nimuleetile umuswamu wangu kunyaakho umuponie, ana lilungu lina likimupeela kiiva mbwibwi.
\v 18 Wiila pina likimukhata, likimugwisa pansi, likimugaha ahumye ilimfulu mu mulomo na kigegejula ameeno, nagu muvili gwiyuuma. Nivalombile avamanyisiwa vaakho kiija validaje ililungu, leelo vagombola.”
\p
\v 19 UYeesu wávayankha wáaja, “Omwe vaanu va shisafi ishi muna musikinihuviilila! Wuli, nisiikhale noomwe mbakha payooli? Nisivagugumile omwe mbakha payooli? Muleeti panu umudiimi uyo.”
\v 20 Vamutwala umudiimi yula kwa Yeesu. Baaho ililungu lyaganile kimwaga uYeesu, lyamugwisiise umudiimi, wáava na malibisi, wáyansa kigalaganda, na kihumya ilimfulu ku mulomo.
\v 21 Baheene uYeesu wámuposiise uwiihe wa mudiimi wáaja, “Ulu lwamuyansaaga yooli?” Uwiihe wa mudiimi wámuyanshile wáaja, “Kihuma pa waana.
\v 22 Wilawiila likimugwisa mu mooto na mu malenga, ulugulumilo lwakwe limubude. Leelo nda ukwiliile kigaha ishiinu shoshoona, utusungupile na kitutanga.”
\v 23 UYeesu wámuyanshile wáaja, “Kwashi wiijova nda nikwiliile? Shila shiinu shikwiliile kwa muunu yula yuna ikiyihuviilila.”
\v 24 Baaho uwiihe wa mudiimi yula wátansiise ishawuti wáaja, “Nayihuviilila! Kiiva ilihuuvi lyangu linangʼana, unitanje niyihuviilile mandu.”
\p
\v 25 UYeesu wáganile kiloleela ishipuga sha vaanu shiyonjelela, baheene wálikhajila ililungu wáaja, “Owe lilungu yuna ukimugaha umudiimi kiiva mbwibwi na mudinde, nikikutawula kiija, muhuma umudiimi uyu, usikhamuyinjilaga khanji!”
\v 26 Ililungu ilyo lyakhoolile inkhoolo, lyamugwisa pansi umudiimi, lyamudegensa mandu, lyahuma. Umudiimi yula wásilikha, avanji vaaja, “Wáafwa!”
\v 27 Leelo uYeesu wámukhata iliwokho, wámunyenyula, umudiimi wáyiima.
\p
\v 28 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vayinjila mu nanda yimonga, pina vakhandi veene duguli vamuposiise vaaja, “Kwashi ose taakunya kilidaga ililungu lila?”
\v 29 UYeesu wámugomosesa wáaja, “Ililungu ngaja lila lisikwiliile kihuma kwa liswi shiishi, mbakha kifuunya.”\f + \fr 9:29 \fq Mbakha kifuunya: \ft Amayandikhwa agamonga amakuulu giyonjelesa amaswi aga, \fqa na kilekha kiilya.\f*
\s UYeesu ilogola khanji shina hambi iifwa na kifyukha
\r (Mataayo 17:22-23; Luuka 9:43-45)
\p
\v 30 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vawuushile pala pina vaali vakwali, vashiliile ku Galilaya. Umwene asadobokhaga umuunu uyunji amanye pina akwali,
\v 31 kiiva akhandi ikivawulanisa vamanyisiwa vaakwe veene duguli. Wávajovela wáaja, “One Lusawo lwa Muunu, nisidoolelwe na kitawulwa ku vaanu vina hambi vikinibuda, leelo ilijuva lya wutatu nikhafyukha.”
\v 32 Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vasamanyaga lina iijova, leelo vatiilaga kimuposa injowo isa kiifwa na kifyukha umwene.
\s Yu naani yuna mukhome mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi
\r (Mataayo 18:1-5; Luuka 9:46-48)
\p
\v 33 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vafishile mu lijumbi lya Kapelinawumu. Pina vakhandi mu nanda yimonga, uYeesu wávaposiise wáaja, “Mwava mukhaanania shishi pina mwava mu nsila?”
\v 34 Leelo aveene vasisimaga tototo, kiiva pina vaali mu nsila vaali vikhaanania kiija yu naani yuna mukhome kuveene.
\p
\v 35 UYeesu wákheele pansi, wávashemeela avamanyisiwa vala ishumi na vavili, wávajovela wáaja, “Umuunu yuna isakula kiiva mukhome isakulwa kiiva munangʼana ku woona, khanji isakulwa avasenjele woona.”
\v 36 Baheene wámutoola umwana umunangʼana, wámuyiimya paakhati, wámukumbaatila, wávajovela wáaja,
\v 37 “Umuunu yoyoona yuna ikimusaajisa umwana umunangʼana ngaja uyu kwa litaawa lyangu, iiva ikinisaajisa one. Khanji yuna ikinisaajisa one, asiiva ikinisaajisa yuune duguli hela, leelo iiva ikimusaajisa yuna wánifilikha one.”
\s Umuunu yuna asili mulugu weesu ali lubali lwesu
\r (Luuka 9:49-50)
\p
\v 38 UYohana wámujovile uYeesu wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji, tamwaga umuunu yumonga ikigadaga amalungu kwa litaawa lyakho, leelo ose tamukhaana kiiva asili wa shipuga sheesu.”
\v 39 UYeesu wáaja, “Musikhamukhaanaji, kiiva kusiina yuna isenga amabikha kwa litaawa lyangu, kuno khanji ikinilogola wuvi one.
\v 40 Umuunu yoyoona yuna asili mulugu weesu, uyo ali lubali lwesu.
\v 41 Umuunu yoyoona yuna ikivapeela ikhoomasi ya malenga kiiva omwe muli vaanu va Mukulusaaji,\f + \fr 9:41 \fq Mukulusaaji: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. Yimba iliswi \fqa Kilisito\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* shiyooli nikivajovela kiija, uNguluvi akhamupeela ulutono lwakwe.”
\s UYeesu imanyisa aga kiyivavala na kihuluta mu //wuumi wa shiluta
\r (Mataayo 18:6-9; Luuka 17:1-2)
\p
\v 42 Avaanu avanangʼana vina vikinihuviilila one, umuunu nda amupinse umunyaayumo waanave agahe uwunansi, yiiva shiba umuunu uyo apinyilisiwe mu nsingo ilyala ilikhome ilya kihawulila na kitaagwa mu shoogo ishitali isha bahali, kulikho kihigwa nu Nguluvi.
\v 43 Iliwokho lyakho nda likikupinsa kigaha uwunansi, lidumula! Shiba kihuluta mu wuumi wa shiluta ni liwokho limo, kulikho kihuluta na mawokho gavili mu malafyo ga mooto gwa shiluta. [\v 44 Umo mumwene muna mangʼonyo gaanave gasiifwa, nu mooto gwa shiluta.]\f + \fr 9:44 \ft Amaswi aga, gakusiina mu mayandikhwa agamonga amakuulu. \f*
\v 45 Iligulu lyakho nda likikupinsa kigaha uwunansi, lidumula! Shiba kihuluta mu wuumi wa shiluta ni ligulu limo, kulikho kitaagwa na magulu gavili mu malafyo ga mooto gwa shiluta. [\v 46 Umo mumwene muna mangʼonyo gaanave gasiifwa, nu mooto gwa shiluta.]\f + \fr 9:46 \ft Amaswi aga, gakusiina mu mayandikhwa agamonga amakuulu.\f*
\v 47 Khanji, iliiho lyakho nda likikupinsa kigaha uwunansi, lijodola! Shiba kihuluta mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi ni liiho limo, kulikho kiiva na meeho goona gavili na kitaagwa mu malafyo ga mooto gwa shiluta.
\v 48 Umo mumwene muna mangʼonyo gaanave gasiifwa, nu mooto gwa shiluta.\f + \fr 9:48 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Isaaya 66:24.\f*
\p
\v 49 “Shila muunu akhavalasiwa nu mooto ngaja shadanda shina shivalasiwa nu muunyo.\f + \fr 9:49 \ft Mu ngʼoma sa Vayahuudi ishadanda shaali shipakhwagwa umuunyo kiija shivalasiwe, baheene shikhandi shinyaanywa pa mooto. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Njowo sa Valaawi 2:13.\f*
\v 50 Umuunyo munofu, leelo nda gunanjishe, usiiponye shishi baheene gukhole? Muveesaje muna muunyo mukhati seenyu,\f + \fr 9:50 \fq Muveesaje muna muunyo mukhati seenyu: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, kiiva ni numbula nofu.\f* baheene musipulinkhane yuumwe kwa yuumwe.”
\c 10
\s UYeesu imanyisa ulwa litwale nu lwa kilekhana
\r (Mataayo 19:1-12; Luuka 16:18)
\p
\v 1 UYeesu wáwuushile pala iiluta ku nyi ya Yudeya na ku mwambwa ya mukhoga gwa Yolodani. Khanji ifipuga fya vaanu vaaluta kwa mwene, wávamanyisa ngaja shina yikhandi ngʼoma yaakwe.
\v 2 Baheene aVafalisaayo vamonga vaaluta kimujela uYeesu vaaja, “Wuli, umugoosi iyiitikhwa kimulekha umudala waakwe?”
\v 3 UYeesu wávagomosesa wáaja, “UMusa wávalajisaaga shishi?”
\v 4 Vamugomosesa vaaja, “UMusa wáyitikhaga mu ndaji kiija, umugoosi amupeelaje umudala waakwe ibalula ya kimulekha.”\f + \fr 10:4 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Luuju lwa Ndaji 24:1.\f*
\p
\v 5 UYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “UMusa wáyandikhaga indaji iyo, kwa kiiva ya numbula seenyu nyuumu.
\v 6 Leelo pashiyanso uNguluvi wávawumbaga umugoosi nu mudala.\f + \fr 10:6 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Shiyanso 1:27.\f*
\v 7 Khanji uNguluvi wáaja, ‘Lino, kwa kiiva ya ilyo, umuunu asimuleshe uwiihe nu maayi waakwe, baheene asiikhale nu mudala waakwe. Vavili ava, vasiive muvili gumo.’ ”
\v 8 Baheene uYeesu wáaja, “Ndeeno ava vasili vavili, leelo vali muvili gumo.\f + \fr 10:8 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Shiyanso 2:24.\f*
\v 9 Kiiva shina wálunganiaga uNguluvi, umuunu asikhabagulaniaga.”
\p
\v 10 Vaganaga kiyinjila khanji mu nanda, avamanyisiwa vaakwe vamuposa ulwa mola iyo.
\v 11 UYeesu wávajovela kiija, “Umuunu yoyoona yuna ikimulekha umudala waakwe iiluta kitoola khanji, iiva wáwaafukha.
\v 12 Woope umudala yuna ikimulekha umugoosi waakwe na kitoolwa nu mugoosi uyunji, iiva mwafu kwa mugoosi uwa wutasi.”
\s UYeesu ikivayimiilila avaana avanangʼana
\r (Mataayo 19:13-15; Luuka 18:15-17)
\p
\v 13 Ilijuva limonga avaanu vakhandi vikimuleetela uYeesu avaana vanangʼana, kiija avaviishile amawokho gaakwe baheene avayimiilile. Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vaganile kilyaga ilyo, vayansa kivakhajila avasafi va vaana.
\v 14 UYeesu wáganaga kivaaga avamanyisiwa vaakwe viigaha ndeeno, wákhalalaga. Wávajovela kiija, “Valeshi avaana avanangʼana vayinse kunyangu, musikhavakhaanaji, kwa kiiva uWutwa wa Nguluvi wuli kwa vaanu vina vali ngaja avaana ava.
\v 15 Shiyooli nikivajovela, umuunu yoyoona yuna asikimuhuviilila uNguluvi ngaja umwana umunangʼana, asikwiliile kiyinjila mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi hata lijuva limo.”
\v 16 Baheene wávakumbaatila avaana vala, wávaviishila amawokho gaakwe, wávayimiilila.
\s Iliposo lya muunu umunya wusi
\r (Mataayo 19:16-26; Luuka 18:18-30)
\p
\v 17 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vayansa kiwuukha, baheene umuunu yumonga wáyinsa luvilo, wáfugama pa Yeesu. Wámuposa uYeesu wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji munofu, nigahe shishi baheene nipate uwuumi wa shiluta?”
\v 18 UYeesu wámugomosesa wáaja, “Kwashi ukinijova kiija nili munofu? Kusiina yuna munofu, leelo yu Nguluvi mwene duguli.
\v 19 Usimeenye indaji sa Nguluvi, ‘Usikhawafukhaga, usikhabudaga, usikhahiijaga, usikhagabedelaga aga wudehi, uvatiilaje uwiiho nu maayi waakho.’\f + \fr 10:19 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Kihuma 20:12-16; Luuju lwa Ndaji 5:16-20.\f*”
\v 20 Umuunu yula wámugomosesa wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji, indaji iso soona nisikheete kihuma uwaana wangu.”
\p
\v 21 UYeesu wámuloleelaga, wámugana, wámujovela wáaja, “Ugayile shiinu shimo. Lutaga uguse ifiinu fyona fina unafyo, ihela sina usiipate, uvagavile avapiina. Nda ugahe ndeeno, usiive wayivishilisa uwusi kwa Nguluvi. Baheene uyinse, unifwataje.”
\v 22 Umuunu yula wáganaga kipulikha ago, wágonja uweeni, wáwuukha pala asugumiilwe, kwa kiiva akhandi ana wusi winshi mandu.
\p
\v 23 UYeesu wávahonekha avaanu koona koona, wávajovela avamanyisiwa vaakwe wáaja, “Lukhamu mandu avanya wusi kiyinjila mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi!”
\v 24 Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vaswiga kwa maswi gaakwe aga wukhamu uwa kihuluta mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi. UYeesu wávajovela khanji wáaja, “Vanangu, lukhamu mandu kihuluta mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi!
\v 25 Lupeefu ingamiya kishila mu mulindi gwa muhonelo, kulikho umunya wusi kiyinjila mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi.”
\p
\v 26 Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vaswijile mandu, vaposeenie kiija, “Lino yu naani yuna akwiliile kikwava uwuumi wa shiluta?”
\v 27 UYeesu wávahonekha, wávajovela wáaja, “Ku vaanu lisikwiliile, leelo kwa Nguluvi likwiliile, kiiva kwa Nguluvi goona gisenjekha.”
\p
\v 28 UPetulo wáyansa kimujovela wáaja, “Loleela, ose tifileshile ifiinu fyona, tikikufwata owe.”
\v 29 UYeesu wáaja, “Shiyooli nikivajovela, shila muunu yuna ayileshile inanda awu umaame awu uwulumbu waakwe awu uwiihe awu umaayi waakwe awu avanaakwe awu amagunda gaakwe kwa kiiva yangu ni Mola iNofu,
\v 30 uyo akhapeelwa ulutono lwa fiinu ifi mala ligana uluhaavi luulu. Akhapeelwa inanda, avamaame, avawulumbu, avanyina, avaana, na magunda. Amalava goope asiipate. Khanji nu luhaavi luna luyinsa akhapeelwa uwuumi wa shiluta.
\v 31 Leelo avaanu vinshi vina vali kuwudugo, vakhava va wutasi. Avaanu vina vali kuwutasi, vakhava va wudugo.”
\s UYeesu ilogola ulwa wutatu shina asiifwe na kifyukha
\r (Mataayo 20:17-19; Luuka 18:31-34)
\p
\v 32 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vakhandi mu nsila viiluta ku Yelusalemu. UYeesu akhandi avalongwele, avamanyisiwa vaakwe na vaanu woona vina vakhandi valongoseenie vaswijile na kitiila. Baheene uYeesu wávatoola khanji vala ishumi na vavili, wáaluta nawo palubali wáyansa kivajovela imola sina sikhasa kimupata.
\v 33 Wáaja, “Puliisi! Tiiluta ku Yelusalemu, ukho kukwene one Lusawo lwa Muunu niiluta kidoolelwa kwa vatambule avakhome na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa. Awo vasinihije kiija nibudwe.
\v 34 Kuwudugo vasinitawule ku vaanu vina vasili Vayahuudi, kiija vanibede, vanitove na majalidi na kinikhomeelela pa musalaaba. Leelo mu lisiku ilya wutatu, nikhafyukha.”
\s Ililombo lya Yaakobo nu Yohana
\r (Mataayo 20:20-28)
\p
\v 35 Baheene uYaakobo nu Yohana, avashina Sebedayo, vamulutiile uYeesu vaaja, “Mumanyisaaji, tilomba utugahile lina tisakula.”
\v 36 UYeesu wávaposa wáaja, “Musakula nivagahile shishi?”
\v 37 Vamugomosesa vaaja, “Pina ukhatema mu Wutwa waakho uwa wutupikho, tilomba na yuuse tive noowe baaho, yumonga akhale ulubali lwakho ulwa kundiilo, uyunji ulubali lwakho ulwa kunshiji.”
\p
\v 38 UYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “Musimeenye gina mwilomba. Wuli, mukwiliile kingʼwelela ikhoomasi iya malava yina nisingʼwelele one, awu mukwiliile kitwinisiwa ulutwinisiwo lwa mfwa luna hambi nitwinisiwa one?”
\v 39 Vamugomosesa vaajova, “Tikwiliile.” UYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “Shiyooli musingʼwelele ikhoomasi iya malava yina one nisiilave, na kiiva mu luhaavi ulukhamu ngaja one.
\v 40 Leelo, kikhala ku liwokho ilya kundiilo awu ilya kunshiji, wusili wutawulilwa wangu. UNguluvi yumwene akhavapeela vina avavishiile shankhaani.”
\p
\v 41 Avamanyisiwa avanji vala ishumi vaganile kipulikha iso, vayansa kivakhalalila uYaakobo nu Yohana.
\v 42 Baheene uYeesu wávashemeela woona, wávajovela wáaja, “Mumeenye kiija avakhome va vaanu va mu nyi iyi, vidobokha kiiva nu wutawulilwa kwa vaanu vaanave, khanji avakhome vaanave vikivakhamiilisa kisenga insengo kwa ngufu.
\v 43 Leelo yisikhaveesaga ndeeno kunyeenyu. Umuunu yoyoona yuna isakula kiiva mukhome kunyeenyu, isakulwa kivasenjela woona.
\v 44 Khanji, umuunu yoyoona yuna isakula kiiva mukhome weenyu, uyo aveesaje ikivasenjela omwe woona.
\v 45 Kiiva one Lusawo lwa Muunu, nisikhayinsile kiija vanisenjele, leelo nayinsaga kivasenjela avaanu na kiwuyasa uwuumi wangu, baheene nivakuluse avaanu vinshi.”
\s UYeesu iiponia umupofu uBatimayo
\r (Mataayo 20:29-34; Luuka 18:35-43)
\p
\v 46 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vaafikha mu lijumbi lya Yeliko. Pina vakhandi viwuukha mu lijumbi lila, vamwajile umupofu yumonga akheele mulubali mu nsila, ilomba ifiinu. Akhandi itambulwa Batimayo, mushina Timayo.
\v 47 Wáganile kipulikha kiija uYeesu uwa ku Nasaleti iishila, wáshemeela kwa shawuti nkhome wáaja, “Owe Yeesu, Lusawo lwa mutwa uDawudi,\f + \fr 10:47 \fq Lusawo lwa mutwa uDawudi: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, \fqa uMukulusaaji\fqa*. Yimba iliswi \fqa Dawudi\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* unisungupile!”
\v 48 Avaanu vinshi vakhandi vikimukhajila kiija asisime, leelo umwene wáyonjelesaaga kishemeela mandu iijova, “Wee Lusawo lwa mutwa uDawudi, unisungupile!”
\p
\v 49 UYeesu wáyiima, wáaja, “Mushemeeli ayinse panu.” Vamushemeela umupofu yula vamujova, “Jimfyaga inumbula! Yiima, ikikushemeela.”
\v 50 Baheene wátaaga umutote gwakwe, wáanyila, wáaluta kwa Yeesu.
\v 51 UYeesu wámuposa wáaja, “Wisakula nikugahile shishi?” Umupofu yula wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji, nisakula kiloleela.”
\v 52 UYeesu wámujovela wáaja, “Lutaga, waapona kiiva wayihuviilila.” Baaho umupofu yula wáloleela, wáyansa kimufwata uYeesu kuna iiluta.
\c 11
\s UYeesu iyinjila ku Yelusalemu kwa filuulu
\r (Mataayo 21:1-11; Luuka 19:28-40; Yohana 12:12-19)
\p
\v 1 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe pina vakhandi nkholeela mu lijumbi lya Yelusalemu, vaafikha ku lujinji lwa Betifage nu lwa Betaniya, ku shidunda shina shikhandi shitambulwa shidunda sha Miseyituni. Baheene wávafilikha avamanyisiwa vaakwe vavili.\fig |lb00087c.jpg|col|||Umupishi gwa museyituni|11:1\fig*
\v 2 Wávajovela wáaja, “Lutaji mu lujinji lula luna luli pamwandi yeenyu. Pina muhuluta mula, baaho musiyaaje inyana dogovi yipinyiilwe, yina yisinajelwajwe kiyangalwa nu muunu. Yiyawulilaji, muyileete panu.
\v 3 Umuunu nda avapose kiija, ‘Mwigaha wuli ndeeni?’ mujovelaji kiija, ‘UMutwa ana nsengo nayo, asigomose pina wásenjela.’”
\p
\v 4 Avamanyisiwa vala vakhayaajile inyana dogovi yiyiimile palubali pa nsila, yikhandi yikunjiilwe pa shikwilo, baheene vayiyawulila.
\v 5 Avaanu vamonga vina vaali nkholeela vavaposiise kiija, “Kwashi mukiyiyawulila inyana dogovi?”
\v 6 Avamanyisiwa vavayanshile shina wávalajisa uYeesu. Avaanu vala vavatawuliile, vawuushile viiluta nayo.
\v 7 Vamutwalila uYeesu inyana dogovi, baheene vatandikha amenda gaanave pa dogovi,\f + \fr 11:7 \fq Dogovi: \ft UYeesu pina wáyangeele idogovi badala ya falaasi, wáwonensaaga avaanu kiija, umwene iyinsa ngaja mutwa wa wulindamafu, asili ngaja mutwa wa kileeta uwulugu.\f* baheene uYeesu wáyangala.
\v 8 Avaanu vinshi vatandikha amenda gaanave mu nsila, vamonga vakhandi viyalaalisa amansamba ga mapishi gina vapanyula mu magunda.
\v 9 Avaanu woona vina valongwele pamwandi na vina vakhandi vifwata kunyuma yaakwe, valogola kwa shawuti nkhome vaaja,
\b
\q “Hosana!\f + \fr 11:9 \fq Hosana: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, \fqa Atunwajwe uNguluvi.\f*
\q Ayimililwajwe yuna iyinsa kwa litaawa lya Mutwa uNguluvi!\f + \fr 11:9 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Sabuli 118:26.\f*
\q
\v 10 Wuyimiililwe uwutwa wa wiheesu uDawudi wuna wiyinsa!
\q Atunwajwe uNguluvi yuna ali kushaanya!”
\b
\p
\v 11 UYeesu wáganile kifikha mu lijumbi lya Yelusalemu, wáyinjila mu lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila.\f + \fr 11:11 \fq Nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* Wáloleelile ifiinu fyona ifya mukhati, leelo kiiva yaali shaamihe, wálutile ku Betaniya lumo na vamanyisiwa vaakwe lishumi na vavili.\fig |lb00250c.jpg|span|||Lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila|11:11\fig*
\s UYeesu ikiguyiijila umujombe
\r (Mataayo 21:18-19)
\p
\v 12 Ulwamilaawu njine pina vaali vahumile ku Betaniya, uYeesu injala yamulumaga.
\v 13 Wágwajile umupishi umujombe kwa kutali guna gwali gulembwile. Wávejeela kiija pamonga asilyaje ilikhomo lyolyona mu mupishi gula. Leelo pina wáfishile asikhalyajile ilikhomo lyolyona, wágaajile mahamba geene, kiiva lusikhandi luhaavi lwa kikhoma amakhomo.
\v 14 UYeesu wágujovile umupishi gula wáaja, “Kihuma iminsiyaano mbakha shiluta, usikhakhoma amakhomo khanji.”\f + \fr 11:14 \fq Usikhakhoma amakhomo khanji: \ft Amakhomo ga mujombe gamanyikhaga mandu na Vayahuudi kiija shihwano. Giwonensa njendo nofu sina uNguluvi wágulumilaga avaanu vaakwe vagahaje. Kiyiijila, panu kiwonensa uwuhigo wa Kilisito kwa Vaisilaheli. \f* Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vapulikhaga sina wájovile.
\s UYeesu ivalasa inanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila
\r (Mataayo 21:12-17; Luuka 19:45-48; Yohana 2:13-22)
\p
\v 15 Pina vafishile ku Yelusalemu, uYeesu wáyinjilaga mu lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila. Pina wáyinjila, wáyansa kivadaga woona vina vakhandi viigusa na kigula ifiinu mula. Wásigalavandula imeesa isa vina vakhandi vibadiilisa ihela na kifigalavandula ifitengo ifya vagusaaji va nkunda.
\v 16 Umwene asamukundaga muunu yoyoona kishilila pa lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila asumwile ishiinu sha kigusa.
\v 17 Baheene uYeesu wávawulaniise avaanu wáaja, “Yiyandiikhwe mu Mayandikhwa aManofu, ‘Inanda yangu yikhava nanda ya mafuunyo ku vaanu woona na vamyanja woona.’\f + \fr 11:17 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Isaaya 56:7.\f* Leelo omwe mwaseetula kiiva ‘wiikhasi wa vahiiji.’\f + \fr 11:17 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Yelemiya 7:11. \f* ”
\p
\v 18 Avatambule avakhome na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa vaganile kipulikha imola iso, vayansa kisakula insila iya kimubuda. Vamutiilaga kiiva ishipuga sha vaanu woona shaswigaga amamanyiso gaakwe.
\v 19 Yaganile kifikha shaamihe, uYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vahumile mu lijumbi.
\s Iliwulaniso lya kimuhuviilila uNguluvi
\r (Mataayo 21:20-22)
\p
\v 20 Pina kwasheele ulwamilaawu, vashiliile pa mujombe gula, vagwajile guyuumile goona kihuma pa ndela.
\v 21 UPetulo wákumbukhaga imola sa mupishi gula, baheene wámujovile uYeesu wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji, loleela umupishi guna wáguyijilaga imihe, guyuumile!”
\p
\v 22 UYeesu wámujovile wáaja, “Muhuvililaga uNguluvi.
\v 23 Shiyooli nikivajovela, umuunu yoyoona nda ashijove ishidunda ishi, shikuulishe, shiyitoose mu bahali, nda ave ikimuhuviilila angaya muninu muninu mu numbula yaakwe kiija, sina wáajova sisenjekha, hambi sisenjekha.
\v 24 Ndeeno nikivajovela kiija, shoshoona shina hambi mwilomba kwa Nguluvi kwa kifuunya, muyihuvililaje kiija mupeelwa, ifyo fisiive fyenyu.
\v 25 Na pina mufuunya, mumusajilaje yoyoona yuna ikivananjila, baheene woope uWiheenyu uwa kushaanya asivasaajile na yuumwe uwunansi weenyu. [\v 26 Nda musikivasaajila avanji vina vikivananjila, uWiheenyu uwa kushaanya asikhavasaajila uwunansi weenyu.]\f + \fr 11:26 \ft Amaswi aga, gakusiina mu mayandikhwa agamonga amakuulu.\f*”
\s UYeesu iposewa ulwa wutawulilwa waakwe
\r (Mataayo 21:23-27; Luuka 20:1-8)
\p
\v 27 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vafishile khanji ku Yelusalemu na vayinjilaga mu lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila. UYeesu pina akhandi ijenda umo, avatambule avakhome, avamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa na vakhome va Vayahuudi vamulutilaga.
\v 28 Vamuposiise kiija, “Aga gina wiigaha, wiigaha kwa wutawulilwa wa naani? Yu naani yuna wákupeela uwutawulilwa uwo?”
\v 29 UYeesu wávayankha wáaja, “Na yuune nisivapose liswi limo. Nda muniyanshe, na yuune nisivajovele kiija, niigaha aga kwa wutawulilwa wa naani.
\v 30 Uwutawulilwa wa Yohana uwa kitwinia wahumaga kwa Nguluvi awu kwa vaanu? Muniyanshe.”
\p
\v 31 Baheene vaposania veene vaaja, “Nda timuyanshe kiija, wahumaga kwa Nguluvi, asitupose kiija, ‘Lino kwashi musikhamuhuviliile?’
\v 32 Khanji nda tijove, ‘Wahumaga kwa vaanu,’ avaanu vasikwiliile kitukunda.” Vakhandi viijova ndeeno, kwa kiiva vakhandi vitiila ishipuga sha vaanu, kiiva woona vakhandi vihuviilila kiija, shiyooli uYohana akhandi mukuwamalago.
\v 33 Baaho vamuyankha vaaja, “Tisimeenye.” Woope uYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “Na yuune nisikivajovela kiija yu naani anipeelile uwutawulilwa uwa kisenga aga.”
\c 12
\s Ishihwano sha valimaaji avadehi
\r (Mataayo 21:33-46; Luuka 20:9-19)
\p
\v 1 UYeesu wáyansa kilogola na vakhome va Vayahuudi kwa fihwano wáaja, “Akhandi akwali umuunu yumonga yuna wálimaga umugunda gwakwe na kivyala amasabiibu. Wápilimya ulukeeke, wákwimba paakhati ililindi ilya kihuujila umulengu gwa masabiibu, khanji wásenga insimbili inali iya kiyiima pashaanya avayangalilaaji. Kuwudugo, wávakhoodesa avalimaaji umugunda gula. Baheene umwene wáshuula.\fig |lb00103c.jpg|span|||Umugunda gwa masabiibu|12:1\fig*
\v 2 Pina lwafikha uluhaavi ulwa kiyava amasabiibu, wámufilikha umuvanda kwa valimaaji vala, kiija amutoolele iligawo lyakwe ilya nkungulo.
\v 3 Leelo avalimaaji vala vamukhata, vamutova na kimudaga bila kimupeela shiinu.
\v 4 Umuunu yula wámufilikha khanji umuvanda uyunji. Uyo woope vamutova inyeeya ku mutwe na kimuyegula.
\v 5 Baheene wámufilikha khanji umuvanda uyunji. Uyo woope vamubuda. Nava vanji vinshi vina vafilikhwagwa, avamonga vatowaagwa, avanji vabudwagwa.
\p
\v 6 “Umunya mugunda uyo wásigala nu muunu yumo uwa kimufilikha, uyo akhandi mwanaakwe umugani. Kuwudugo wámufilikha yuuyo, wáaja, ‘Uyu mwanangu, vasimutiile.’
\v 7 Leelo avalimaaji vala vajovelana vaajova, ‘Uyu yumwene umunya kihaala umugunda ugu. Lino, timubude, baheene uwuhaasi waakwe wuve weesu.’
\v 8 Baheene vamukhata, vamubuda, vamutaaga kunja ya mugunda.”
\p
\v 9 Baheene uYeesu wávaposa wáaja, “Lino muhiiva umunya mugunda yula asivagahe shi avalimaaji vala? Asiyinse kivabuda, nagu mugunda gula asivakhoodese avaanu vanji.
\v 10 Wuli, musinayimbe iliswi ili? Yiyandiikhwe mu Mayandikhwa aManofu kiija,
\q ‘Ilingʼanga lina avasengaaji valikhaanaga,\f + \fr 12:10 \fq Ilingʼanga lina avasengaaji valikhaanaga: \ft UYeesu pina ilogola amaswi aga Lufingo uLukuulu, apo iiva ikiyijova yumwene.\f*
\q lilyene liveele lingʼanga likhome ilya ku mbogonyo ya luutu lwa nanda.
\q
\v 11 UMutwa uNguluvi yumwene wáagaha ilyo,
\q lyope lya miitu kunyeesu.’\f + \fr 12:10-11 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Sabuli 118:22-23.\f*”
\p
\v 12 Avakhome va Vayahuudi vala vasakulaga insila ya kimukhata, kiiva vamanyaga kiija, ishihwano shila shikhandi shikivajova vaveene. Leelo vamulekha, vawuukha kwa kiiva vashitiilaga ishipuga sha vaanu.
\s AVafalisaayo vikimujela uYeesu ulwa kihomba ikhoodi
\r (Mataayo 22:15-22; Luuka 20:20-26)
\p
\v 13 Baheene avakhome vala vavafilikhaga aVafalisaayo avanji na vanandeje va mutwa uHelode, kiija valute vamusigame uYeesu mu maswi gina ilogola.
\v 14 Vamulutila vamujova kiija, “Mumanyisaaji, timeenye kiija owe uli muunu wa shiyooli. Usikimutiila muunu, hata umuunu yuna ana nsengo nkhome, leelo wimanyisa insila ya Nguluvi mu shiyooli. Wuli, indaji sa Musa sikitutawula kihomba ikhoodi kwa Kayisaali, umutwa wa Valuumi, awu ndaali? Tihombaje awu tisikhahombaga?”
\p
\v 15 Leelo uYeesu wámanyaga uwumyansi waanave, wávajovela wáaja, “Kwashi mukinijela? Nipeeli isilinje niyiloleele.”\fig |hk00166c.jpg|col|||Isilinje|12:15\fig*
\v 16 Vamupeela. Woope wávaposa wáaja, “Ishimanyilo ishi na mayandikhwa aga gina gakwali mu silinje iyi, ga naani?” Aveene vamugomosesa vaaja, “Ga Kayisaali, umutwa wa Valuumi.”
\v 17 Baaho uYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “Ifya Kayisaali mupeelaji uKayisaali, ifya Nguluvi mupeelaji uNguluvi.” Woona vaswiga mandu.
\s Ulufyukho lwa vina vafwile
\r (Mataayo 22:23-33; Luuka 20:27-40)
\p
\v 18 Baheene aVasadukaayo,\f + \fr 12:18 \fq AVasadukaayo: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Vasadukaayo\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* vina vakhandi viija kusiina kifyukha vina vafwile, vaaluta kwa Yeesu, vamuposa vaaja,
\v 19 “Wee Mumanyisaaji, uMusa wátuyandishilaga indaji kiija, umuunu nda afwe na kimulekha umudala angaya mwana, yisakulwa umaame amuhaale umufwile uyo, baheene amusavile avaana umaame yuna wáfwisaga.\f + \fr 12:19 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Luuju lwa Ndaji 25:5-10.\f*
\v 20 Lino, vakhandi vakwali avamaame fungati vina vakhandi vaana va wiihe yumo. Uwa wutasi wátoola umudala, wáafwa angaya mwana.
\v 21 Uwa wuvili wámuhaala umufwile yula, woope wáafwa angaya mwana. Kuunyuma uwa wutatu, woope wámuhaala, wáafwa. Yaava shishila ku woona fungati.
\v 22 Avaanu woona vala vamutoolaga umudala yula, leelo woona vafwisaga bila kilekha umwana.
\v 23 Lino wuli, ilisiku lya kifyukha avaanu woona, umufwile yula akhava mudala wa naani? Kiiva wátolwagwa na vagoosi woona fungati!”
\p
\v 24 UYeesu wávayanshile wáaja, “Omwe muyajile, kiiva musiimanya aMayandikhwa aManofu na musiimanya ingufu sa Nguluvi.
\v 25 Kiiva pina vakhafyukha vina vafwile, kukhava kusiina kitoola wala kitoolwa, leelo vakhava ngaja avamalayikha vina vali kwa Nguluvi.
\v 26 Leelo imola ya kifyukha vina vafwile, wuli, musiyimbile mu litaafili lya Musa, pina uNguluvi wáyiwonensiise kwa Musa pala pa musita pina pakhandi piveekha umooto?\f + \fr 12:26 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Kihuma 3:6.\f* UNguluvi wámujovile wáaja, ‘One yuune Nguluvi wa Abulahamu, Nguluvi wa Isaaka, khanji Nguluvi wa Yaakobo.’\f + \fr 12:26 \fq One yuune Nguluvi wa Abulahamu, Nguluvi wa Isaaka, khanji Nguluvi wa Yaakobo: \ft Avagosiivaha ava hata nda vafwile maakha minshi gina gashilile, vakhandi wuumi vali lumo nu Nguluvi, vahepeleese ulufyukho lwa mavili gaanave.\f*
\v 27 Umwene asili Nguluvi wa vina vafwile, leelo Nguluvi wa vina wuumi.\f + \fr 12:27 \fq Umwene asili Nguluvi wa vina vafwile, leelo Nguluvi wa vina wuumi: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, uAbulahamu, uIsaaka, nu Yaakobo vapili wuumi, vali lumo nu Nguluvi kushaanya. \f* Omwe muyajile mandu.”
\s UYeesu iganula indaji inkhome
\r (Mataayo 22:34-40; Luuka 10:25-28)
\p
\v 28 Umumanyisaaji wa ndaji sa Musa yumonga akhandi bahala, ikivapuliisa aVasadukaayo vikhaanania nu Yeesu. Wámwajile kiija uYeesu ikivayankha wunofu, woope wámuposa uYeesu wáaja, “Ndaji nshi inkhome mu ndaji soona?”
\p
\v 29 UYeesu wámuyanshile wáaja, “Indaji inkhome ku soona yiyeene iyi, ‘Puliisa Isilaheli, uMutwa uNguluvi weesu ali yumo mwene.
\v 30 Umuganaje uMutwa uNguluvi waakho kwa numbula yaakho yoona, kwa mahiiva gaakho goona, kwa luhala lwakho loona na kwa ngufu saakho soona.’\f + \fr 12:29-30 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Luuju lwa Ndaji 6:4-5.\f*
\v 31 Indaji ya wuvili yiija, ‘Umuganaje umuyaago ngaja shina uyiganile yuuwe.’\f + \fr 12:31 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Njowo sa Valaawi 19:18.\f* Kusiina indaji iyinji inkhome kishila isi.”
\p
\v 32 Baheene umumanyisaaji wa ndaji yula wáaja, “Shiyooli Mumanyisaaji! Owe waajova wunofu kiija, uNguluvi ali yumo mwene, kusiina uyunji, yumwene yuuyo.
\v 33 Lunofu kimugana umwene kwa numbula yoona, kwa luhala loona na kwa ngufu soona, na kimugana umuyaago ngaja shina uyiganile yuuwe. Kisenga ndeeno lunofu kishila kihumya ifyadanda fyona fina fipembelesewa kwa Nguluvi.”
\v 34 UYeesu pina wáweene yula umumanyisaaji wámuyankha kwa luhala wámujovile wáaja, “Owe usili kutali kiyinjila mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi.” Kihuma uluhaavi ulo, asajelile umuunu kimuposa iliposo lyolyona.
\s UMukulusaaji mwana wa naani?
\r (Mataayo 22:41-46; Luuka 20:41-44)
\p
\v 35 UYeesu pina akhandi ikivamanyisa mu lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila, wáposiise wáaja, “Kwashi avamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa viija Mukulusaaji yuna uNguluvi wátahisaaga kimufilikha,\f + \fr 12:35 \fq Mukulusaaji yuna uNguluvi wátahisaaga kimufilikha: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. Yimba iliswi \fqa Kilisito\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* Lusawo lwa mutwa uDawudi?
\v 36 UDawudi yumwene pina wálongoseewe nu Numbula uMunofu wájovile ndeeni,
\q ‘UMutwa uNguluvi wámujeele uMutwa wangu,
\q “Khala ku liwokho lyangu ilya kundiilo,
\q mbakha pina nikhava nakutanga
\q uvamene avalugu vaakho na kivatema.” ’\f + \fr 12:36 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Sabuli 110:1.\f* ”
\p
\v 37 UYeesu wáyitenekha wáaja, “Nda uDawudi yumwene ikimutambula uMukulusaaji kiija Mutwa, lino uMukulusaaji\f + \fr 12:37 \fq UMukulusaaji: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. \f* akwiliile wuli kiiva mwanaakwe?” Ishipuga ishikhome sha vaanu shapulisiise kwa wushendeefu.
\s UYeesu ikivapavila avaanu kwa vamanyisaaji va ndaji
\r (Mataayo 23:1-36; Luuka 20:45-47)
\p
\v 38 UYeesu mu mamanyiso gaakwe wájovile, “Muyivavalaje na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa. Vidobokha kijenda jenda vafwalile inkhansu inali na kihunjilwa na vaanu kwa kitiilwa pa munaada.
\v 39 Pina vali mu nanda isa kifuunyila, visakula kikhala mu fitengo ifya kumwandi. Mu fiwungo, viikhala mu fitengo ifya kitiilwa.
\v 40 Avaanu ava viipokha ifiinu ifya vina vafwiliilwe! Khanji mu wumyansi waanave, vifuunya amafuunyo matali, baheene avaanu vave vikivaaga vagolofu. Ilijuva lya mukhole, uNguluvi akhavalafya mandu.”
\s Isadaakha ya mufwile umupiina
\r (Luuka 21:1-4)
\p
\v 41 UYeesu pina wáali mu lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila, wákheele iloleela ishombo sha kihumisa isadaakha. Apo akhandi iloleela avaanu vinshi vina vaali vihumyaga isadaakha. Avanya wusi vinshi vakhandi viihumya ihela nyinshi.
\v 42 Uluhaavi ulo wáyinsa uwashimaayi umufwile khanji mupiina, wáahumya isilinje sivili.
\v 43 Baaho uYeesu wávashemeela avamanyisiwa vaakwe wávajovela wáaja, “Shiyooli nikivajovela, uwashimaayi uyu umufwile khanji mupiina, wáahumya kishila woona.
\v 44 Kiiva avanji woona awo vaahumya fisheefu mu fiinu fyanave ifinshi. Leelo uwashimaayi umufwile uyu mu wupiina waakwe, wáahumya fyona fina ikiyihuviilila mu wiikhasi waakwe.”
\c 13
\s UYeesu iikuva amalago ulwa kibomolwa //inanda imbaagule
\r (Mataayo 24:1-2; Luuka 21:5-6)
\p
\v 1 UYeesu akhandi iihuma pa lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila, umumanyisiwa waakwe yumonga wámujovile wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji, loleela amangʼanga aga ni nanda isi shina sa luswigo.”
\v 2 UYeesu wámuyanshile wáaja, “Nikivajovela kiija shina mukisaaga inanda inkhome isi, sisikhasigala. Kiiva kusiina ilingʼanga lina likhasigala pashaanya ya lingʼanga liyine. Goona ago gakhagwisiwa.”\f + \fr 13:2 \fq Goona ago gakhagwisiwa: \ft Inanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila yabomolwagwa na Valuumi umwakha gwa mashumi fungati pina wásawaagwa uYeesu Kilisito. \f*
\s Amalava amakhome gina gakhayinsa
\r (Mataayo 24:3-14; Luuka 21:7-19)
\p
\v 3 UYeesu akhandi akheele pa shidunda sha Miseyituni, wáali aloleelile ku nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila. Apo uPetulo, uYaakobo, uYohana nu Andeleya, vakhandi veene duguli nu Yeesu, vamuposiise vaaja,
\v 4 “Tilomba utujovele, inanda isi sikhagwisiwa yooli? Shimanyilo shishi shina shikhatuwulanisa kiija, uluhaavi ulwa kisenjekha aga goona luli nkholeela?”
\p
\v 5 Baheene uYeesu wávajovela wáaja, “Muveesaje meeho, asilaave avajanje muunu yoyoona.
\v 6 Kiiva vakhayinsa avaanu vinshi kwa litaawa lyangu vakhajova, ‘One yuune Mukulusaaji.’\f + \fr 13:6 \fq Mukulusaaji: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. Yimba iliswi \fqa Kilisito\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* Woope vakhava vikivajanga avaanu vinshi.
\v 7 Omwe pina mukhapulikha imola ni pwepwesi sa wulugu, musikhatungumalaji. Ago goona mbakha gawoneshe, leelo uluhaavi ulwa wudugo lukhava lushaanali.
\v 8 Insiku iso inyi yimo yikhalwa ni nyi iyinji, uwutwa wukhalwa nu wutwa uwunji. Kukhava mudegenkho imbali nyinshi, nayi njala yikhagwa. Ago goona gakhava ngaja shiyanso sha wuvafi uwa washimaayi pina ali nkholeela kisava.
\p
\v 9 “Omwe yivavalaji, kiiva vakhavatwala pa livansa lya vakhome, khanji vakhavatova mu nanda isa kifuunyila. Vakhavatwala omwe pa vakhome va nyi na pa vatwa, kwa kiiva yangu. Baheene muve mukivabedela.
\v 10 Leelo tangusiina iMola iNofu yisakulwa yikhomwe mu nyi soona.
\v 11 Pina vakhavakhata na kivatwala pa livansa, musikhatungumalaji kiija mukhalogola shishi awu mukhalogola wuli. Kiiva uluhaavi ulo, uNguluvi akhavapeela aga kilogola, kwa kiiva musili yuumwe muna mulogola, leelo iiva yu Numbula uMunofu.
\p
\v 12 “Kwa luhaavi ulo, umuunu akhamudoolela ulukholo lwakwe kwa valugu kiija abudwe. Khanji, uwiihe akhamudoolela umwanaakwe kwa valugu kiija abudwe. Avaana woope vakhavadoolela avasafi vaanave kiija vabudwe.
\v 13 Avaanu woona vakhavakhalalila kwa kiiva omwe muli vamanyisiwa vangu. Leelo umuunu yoyoona yuna akhajimba mbakha kuwudugo, uNguluvi akhamukulusa.
\s Amalava amakhome gina gakhayinsa
\r (Mataayo 24:15-28; Luuka 21:20-24)
\p
\v 14 “Ino, mu luhaavi ulo mukhashaaga ‘ishiinu shina shikhalasa’ shiyiimile uluvala ulwa panofu. Yuna iyimba amanyaje.\f + \fr 13:14 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Daniyeli 9:27; 11:31; 12:11.\f* Pina mukhagaaga amaswi aga, vala vina vali ku nyi ya Yudeya vasijilaje ku fidunda.
\v 15 Umuunu yuna ali pashaanya ya nanda, asikhayiikhaga na kiyinjila mu nanda yaakwe kitoola shoshoona.
\v 16 Woope yuna ali ku mugunda asikhagomokhaga kukhaaya kitoola umutote gwakwe.
\v 17 Leelo aka, vina vakhava vana lwanda na vina vakhava viyonsa mu nsiku iso!
\v 18 Mufuunyaje kiija ago galeshe kiyinsa uluhaavi lwa shipepo,
\v 19 kiiva mu luhaavi ulo, avaanu vakhapata amalava makhome mandu gina gasinawonekhaje kaa, kihuma pina uNguluvi wáwumbile inyi mbakha iminsiyaano. Khanji amalava ago, gasikhawonekha kaa.
\v 20 UNguluvi nda akhalekha kisheepusa insiku iso isa malava, kukhava kusiina umuunu yuna akhakulukha kiifwa. Leelo kwa kiiva ya vabaagule vaakwe, uNguluvi akhasisheepusa insiku iso.
\p
\v 21 “Lino mu luhaavi ulo, umuunu nda ikivajovela kiija, ‘Loleela, uMukulusaaji\f + \fr 13:21 \fq UMukulusaaji: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. \f* ali apa!’ Awu ‘Ali kula!’ musikhahuvililaga.
\v 22 Kiiva vakhayinsa avakuwamalago avadehi na vaanu vina vakhava viijova uwudehi kiija, aveene vakulusaaji. Awo vakhava viigaha amabikha ga miitu, baheene vakhavajanga avaanu na kiija, nda yikwiliile vavajanje hata avabaagule va Nguluvi.
\v 23 Lino muveesaje meeho, kiiva navajovela nkhaani goona ago, pina uluhaavi lusinaafishe.
\s Kiyinsa khanji kwa Lusawo lwa Muunu
\r (Mataayo 24:29-31; Luuka 21:25-28)
\p
\v 24 “Insiku siiso, gakhasa kishila amalava ago,
\q ‘Ilijuva likhaseetulwa nshiisi,
\q nagu mwesi gusikhangʼaala khanji.’
\q
\v 25 ‘Inondwe sikhagwa kihuma kushaanya,
\q nafi fiinu fina fili kushaanya fikhadegenkha.’\f + \fr 13:25 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Isaaya 13:10; 34:4; Yoheli 2:10.\f*
\p
\v 26 “Apo woona vakhanyaaga one Lusawo lwa Muunu niyinsa mu mafunde ni ngufu nyinshi nu wutupikho.\f + \fr 13:26 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Daniyeli 7:13. \f*
\v 27 Baheene nikhavafilikha avamalayikha vangu, woope vakhavakungaania avabaagule vangu kihuma imbali soona isa nyi, kihuma kuwudugo wa nyi nu wa kushaanya.
\s Ishihwano sha mujombe
\r (Mataayo 24:32-35; Luuka 21:29-33)
\p
\v 28 “Yimanyisaaji ishihwano kihuma ku mujombe. Kwa kiiva nda amansamba na mahamba galembwile, baheene mwimanya kiija, uluhaavi lwa mingo luli nkholeela.
\v 29 Shiisho ndeeno, na yuumwe pina mukhagaaga ago gisenjekha, manyaji kiija, one Lusawo lwa Muunu nili nkholeela kiyinsa.
\v 30 Shiyooli nikivajovela kiija, ishisafi ishi shisikhashila mbakha aga goona pina gakhava gasenjekha.
\v 31 Uwulanga ni nyi fikhashila, leelo amaswi gangu gakhava ga shiluta.
\s Kusiina yuna ameenye uluhaavi ulwa kiyinsa uYeesu
\r (Mataayo 24:36-44)
\p
\v 32 “Leelo ulwa lijuva lila nu lwa luhaavi lula, kusiina umuunu yuna iimanya hata avamalayikha va kushaanya wala Lusawo lwa Nguluvi, leelo yu Daada mwene duguli yuna ameenye.
\v 33 Kiiva musimeenye uluhaavi ulo lukhayinsa yooli, yipinyangaji na muveesaje meeho.
\p
\v 34 “Yisiive ngaja umuunu yuna wáshuulile. Baheene wáyilekha inanda yaakwe mu mawokho ga vavanda, shila muunu wámupeelaga insengo yaakwe. Khanji wámulajiise umuyangalilaaji wa nanda kiija, ave meeho.
\v 35 Lino muveesaje meeho, kiiva musiimanya uluhaavi lwa kiwuya umunya nanda.\f + \fr 13:35 \fq Umunya nanda: \ft UYeesu ikiyitambula kiija yumwene munya nanda.\f* Pamonga asiyinse shaamihe, awu paashilo paakhati, awu pina kuhenga awu palwamilaawu.
\v 36 Muveesaje meeho, nda ayinse avatilimbule asilaave avaaje mugoneleele.
\v 37 Iliswi lina nisakula kivajovela omwe, lilyene lina nikivajovela avaanu woona kiija, vaveesaje meeho.”
\c 14
\s Ulupulinkhano ulwa kimubuda uYeesu
\r (Mataayo 26:1-5; Luuka 22:1-2; Yohana 11:45-53)
\p
\v 1 Saali sisigeele nsiku sivili kiiva shiwungo sha Pasaakha\f + \fr 14:1 \fq Pasaakha: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* na shiwungo sha makhaate gina gasiponyisiiwe ishiwumulilo.\f + \fr 14:1 \fq Shiwungo sha makhaate gina gasiponyisiiwe ishiwumulilo: \ft Yimba iliswi ili mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* Avatambule avakhome na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa, vakhandi visakula insila iya kimukhata uYeesu kwa jiila, kiija vamubude.
\v 2 Vajovelanaga veene vaaja, “Tisikhamukhataga ilisiku lya shiwungo, kiiva avaanu vasilaave valeete ilibaatu.”
\s UYeesu idudumisiwa amafuta ku Betaniya
\r (Mataayo 26:6-13; Yohana 12:1-8)
\p
\v 3 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vakhandi mu lujinji lwa ku Betaniya, mu nanda ya Simoni yuna ulwamwandi akhandi ana nyawulova. UYeesu pina akhandi akheele iilya, uwashimaayi yumonga wáyinjiile ni nsupa ya mafuta aga lifungu likhome, gina ginunshilila mandu. Wádindula insupa, baheene wámududumisisa uYeesu ku mutwe.
\v 4 Avaanu vamonga vina vaali apo vakhaleele vaaja, “Vayaa! Kwashi iveyanga ndeeni?
\v 5 Kiiva amafuta aga, ndi gagusiwa kwa hela nyinshi mandu,\f + \fr 14:5 \fq Hela nyinshi mandu: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe, \fqa dinaali magana gatatu (300). \ft Ihela isi silingeene na mahombo ga nsiku magana gatatu (300). \f* na kivapeela avapiina.” Baheene vamukhajilaga uwashimaayi yula.
\p
\v 6 Leelo uYeesu wáaja, “Muleshi. Kwashi mukimulafya uwashimaayi uyu? Kiiva wánigahila amanofu mandu.
\v 7 Avapiina muli lumo nsiku soona, pina musakula mukwiliile kivatanga luhaavi loloona. Leelo one nisiiva lumo noomwe nsiku soona.
\v 8 Uwashimaayi uyu wásenga lina akwiliile kisenga. Wáatala kinidudumisisa amafuta umuvili gwangu kwa masiilo.
\v 9 Shiyooli nikivajovela, popoona pina iMola iNofu yikhakhomwa mu nyi soona, gakhalogolwa amanofu goona gina uwashimaayi uyu wánigahila, baheene avaanu vakhamukumbukha.”
\s UYuuda uIsikaliyoote iyiitikha kimudoolela uYeesu
\r (Mataayo 26:14-16; Luuka 22:3-6)
\p
\v 10 UYuuda uIsikaliyoote, umunyaayumo mu vamanyisiwa vala ishumi na vavili va Yeesu, wálutile kwa vatambule avakhome kiija, amudoolele uYeesu kuveene.
\v 11 Aveene vaganile kipulikha imola iso, vashendeeva mandu vapulinkhana na woope kimupeela ihela. Baheene uYuuda uIsikaliyoote wáyansa kisakula imwenshe inofu iya kimudoolela uYeesu.
\s UYeesu iilya ishakiilya sha Pasaakha na vamanyisiwa vaakwe
\r (Mataayo 26:17-25; Luuka 22:7-14, 21-23; Yohana 13:21-30)
\p
\v 12 Ilisiku lya wutasi ilya shiwungo sha makhaate gina gasiponyisiiwe ishiwumulilo, pina aVayahuudi vakhandi vikisishinja inyana nkholo sina sikhandi sivishiilwe kwa kiiva ya shiwungo sha Pasaakha, avamanyisiwa va Yeesu vamuposiise vaaja, “Wisakula tikunosese kwi, ishakiilya sha shiwungo sha Pasaakha?”
\v 13 Baheene uYeesu wávafilikha vavili mu vamanyisiwa vaakwe, wáaja, “Lutaji ku Yelusalemu, ukho musitangaane nu mugoosi yumonga, avegeele injiilo ya malenga. Uyo yumwene mumufwataje,
\v 14 mbakha ilitembe lina hambi iyinjila. Apo mujovelaji umunya litembe kiija, ‘UMumanyisaaji iijova, “Wuli kwi uwudaama wa vahensa, wuna nikwiliile kiliila ishakiilya sha shiwungo sha Pasaakha lumo na vamanyisiwa vangu?”’
\v 15 Baheene umwene asivasoonele uwudaama uwukhome uwa pa juulu wuna wuvishiilwe pa kikhala. Umo mumwene mutunosese.”
\v 16 Avamanyisiwa vala vawuukha, vaaluta ku lijumbi ilyo. Vaganaga kifikha, vagaaga goona ngaja shina uYeesu akhandi avajoveele, baheene vashinosa ishakiilya sha shiwungo sha Pasaakha.
\p
\v 17 Shaganile kifikha ishaamihe, uYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe ishumi na vavili vaafikha mu nanda yila.
\v 18 Pina viilya, uYeesu wáajova, “Shiyooli nikivajovela kiija, umunyaayumo weenyu yuna iilya noone, asinidoolele.”
\v 19 Avamanyisiwa vaakwe vasugumilwa, shila muunu wáyansa kiyiposa kwa Yeesu, “Wuli, yuune?”
\v 20 Umwene wáaja, “Umuunu uyo, wa mu shipuga sheenyu, omwe ishumi na vavili, yuna idabisa umukhaate lumo noone mu bakuli.
\v 21 One Lusawo lwa Muunu nikhabudwa ngaja shina yiyandiikhwe mu Mayandikhwa aManofu. Leelo aka, umuunu yuna akhanidoolela. Shiba yaali yive umuunu uyo wáali ave asisaviilwe!”
\s IShakiilya sha Mutwa
\r (Mataayo 26:26-30; Luuka 22:14-20; 1 Vakolinto 11:23-25)
\p
\v 22 Woope pina viliisaga, uYeesu wátoola umukhaate, wámuhonjesa uNguluvi, wágumenyulania, wávapeela avamanyisiwa vaakwe wáaja, “Tooli, ugu gugwene muvili gwangu.”
\v 23 Baheene wátoola ikhoomasi ya divaayi, wámuhonjesa uNguluvi, wávapeela, woona vaangʼwa.
\v 24 Wávajovela wáaja, “Ishi, shimanyilo sha lufingo\f + \fr 14:24 \fq Lufingo: \ft Ulu lukundano lwa mbali sivili, yikwiliile kiiva ya vaanu vavili, fipuga fivili hata uNguluvi na vaanu vaakwe. Yimba iliswi \fqa Lufingo\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* ulupya luna lusenjekha kwa danda yangu. Khanji yikunukha kwa kiiva ya vaanu vinshi.
\v 25 Shiyooli nikivajovela kiija, nisikhangʼwa khanji idivaayi, mbakha mu lijuva lina nikhangʼwa idivaayi imya mu Wutwa wa Nguluvi.”
\v 26 Vaganile kiyeyema,\f + \fr 14:26 \fq Vaganile kiyeyema: \ft Pina vaalya ishakiilya sha Pasaakha, aVayahuudi vakhandi ni ngʼoma ya kiyeyema iSabuli 113-118.\f* vawuukha viiluta ku shidunda sha Miseyituni.
\s UYeesu ikimujova uPetulo kiija akhamukhaana
\r (Mataayo 26:31-35; Luuka 22:31-34; Yohana 13:36-38)
\p
\v 27 UYeesu wávajovela avamanyisiwa vaakwe wáaja, “Omwe woona mukhanisiga, kiiva yiyandiikhwe kiija, ‘Nikhamutova umudimaaji wa nkholo, ishipuga sha nkholo shikhapalankhana.’\f + \fr 14:27 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Sekhaliya 13:7.\f*
\v 28 “Leelo pina nafyukha, nikhavalongola kiluta ku Galilaya.”
\p
\v 29 UPetulo wámujovela wáaja, “Hata nda woona vakuleshe, one nisikikulekha kaa!”
\v 30 UYeesu wámujovela wáaja, “Shiyooli nikikujovela kiija, ishilo ishi injogolo pina yisinaavishe ulwa wuvili, owe usiive wanikhaana mala khatatu.”
\v 31 Leelo uPetulo wáajova kwa kiyikhangasa wáaja, “Hata nda yive kiifwa lumo noowe, nisikulekha kaa.” Woope avamanyisiwa avanji woona vaajova shiisho.
\s UYeesu ikimufuunya uNguluvi mu Getisemane
\r (Mataayo 26:36-46; Luuka 22:39-46)
\p
\v 32 UYeesu na vamanyisiwa vaakwe vafishile pa shiisi shina shitambulwa Getisemane. Baheene wávajovela wáaja, “Mukhale bahanu pina one nifuunya.”
\v 33 Wávatoola uPetulo, uYaakobo nu Yohana, baheene wáaluta nawo. Wáyansa kisugumilwa na kilava mandu.
\v 34 Wávajovela wáaja, “Inumbula yangu yisugumiilwe mandu nkholeela na kiifwa. Mukhale baaha, muveesaje meeho.”
\p
\v 35 Umwene wáwuukha wáaluta pamwandi padoodo, wáagwa pansi wágubama, wámufuunya uNguluvi wáaja, “Nda yikwiliile, nikikulomba uluhaavi ulwa malava lwali lunihegushe.”
\v 36 Wáaja, “Aba,\f + \fr 14:36 \fq Aba: \ft Liswi lya Shialaamu. Ishi shilogolo sha Yeesu. Uluganulo lwakwe, \fqa Daada.\f* Daada, owe kusiina lina wigombola. Nikikulomba uniwuusise ikhoomasi iyi iya malava aga, leelo yisikhaveesaga shina nisakula one, leelo yive shina wisakula owe.”
\p
\v 37 Wáganile kihuma kifuunya, wávaajile avamanyisiwa vatatu vagoneleele utulo. Baheene wámuposa uPetulo wáaja, “Simoni, ugoneleele? Ugombwele kiiva meeho hata lisala limo?”
\v 38 Baheene wávajovela wáaja, “Muveesaje meeho, mufuunyaji uNguluvi kiija, avatanje musikhagahaga uwunansi pina mwijelwa. Mwidobokha kigaha wunofu, leelo umuvili muwoto.”
\p
\v 39 UYeesu wálutile kifuunya khanji, wáwuyiila kifuunya maswi gagala.
\v 40 Wáganile kifuunya wágomokha khanji, wávaaga vagoneleele, kiiva vakhandi vana tulo tusito. Vasikhandi ni liswi lya kimugomosesa.
\p
\v 41 Wáaluta khanji kifuunya ulwa wutatu. Wáganile kitina wávajovela wáaja, “Mushaanali mupigonile utulo na kituuya? Ino lwakwila! Uluhaavi lwangu ulwa malava lwafikha. Lino one Lusawo lwa Muunu, nisikhatwe na kitwalwa mu mawokho ga vanansi.
\v 42 Yiimaji, tilutaje! Loleeli, yuna ikinidoolela ali nkholeela.”
\s UYeesu iikhatwa
\r (Mataayo 26:47-56; Luuka 22:47-53; Yohana 18:3-12)
\p
\v 43 UYeesu pina akhandi ashaanali ilogola, shitu wátwiwukha uYuuda umunyaayumo mu vamanyisiwa vaakwe ishumi na vavili, wáyinsa ni shipuga sha vaanu shina shikhandi ni panga ni ndulugu. Ishipuga isho shafilikhwagwa na vatambule avakhome, avamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa na vakhome va Vayahuudi.
\v 44 UYuuda umudolelaaji wávajovelaga nkhaani avaanu vala ishimanyilo isha kimumanya uYeesu kiija, “Yula yuna hambi nikimunoonela, uyo iiva yumwene. Mukhataji na kiwuukha nawo, muyangalilaji.”
\p
\v 45 UYuuda wáganile kifikha wámuhejeela uYeesu wáaja, “Mumanyisaaji.” Wámunoonela.
\v 46 Baheene avaanu vala vamukhata uYeesu.
\v 47 Umuyaanave yumonga mu vina vakhandi vayiimile lumo nu Yeesu, wátoola ipanga na kimudumula ilikutu umuvanda wa mutambule umukhome.
\p
\v 48 UYeesu wávaposa avaanu vala wáaja, “Kwashi muniyinsiile ni panga ni ndulugu kinikhata one ngaja muyinsile kimukhata muhiiji? Wuli, mwihiiva kiija one nikiyikhaana iselekhaali?
\v 49 Nsiku soona tikhandi lumo noomwe, nikhandi nimanyisa mu lukeeke lwa nanda imbaagule iya kifuunyila, leelo musikhanikheete. Leelo aga goona gasenjekha, kiija gakwilane gina gayandiikhwe mu Mayandikhwa aManofu.”
\p
\v 50 Baheene avamanyisiwa vaakwe woona vamulekha, vaasiga.
\v 51 Kukhandi kuna mujeleelo yumonga yuna wáali ayitoteeshe umutote hela, akhandi ikimufwata uYeesu. Woope visakulaga kimukhata,
\v 52 leelo umwene wápulumukhaga mu mawokho, wágulekha umutote gwakwe, wáasiga bwinda.
\s UYeesu pa livansa lya Vayahuudi
\r (Mataayo 26:57-68; Luuka 22:54-55, 63-71; Yohana 18:13-14, 19-24)
\p
\v 53 Baheene avaanu vala vamutwala uYeesu kwa mutambule umukhome.\f + \fr 14:53 \fq Mutambule umukhome: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Vatambule \ft mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* Ukho vakungaana avatambule avakhome woona, avakhome va Vayahuudi na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa.
\v 54 UPetulo akhandi ikimufwata uYeesu kwa kutali. Wáyinjila mu lukeeke lwa nanda ya mutambule umukhome, wáakhala lumo na vayangalilaaji, wáava iyoota umooto.
\p
\v 55 Baheene avatambule avakhome na vakhome va livansa lyona ilya Vayahuudi,\f + \fr 14:55 \fq Livansa lyona ilya Vayahuudi: \ft Yimba iliswi \fqa Livansa lya Vayahuudi\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* vakhandi visakula uwulunjikhaaji wa kimuhiga uYeesu, kiija vamubude. Leelo vasikhawupatile.
\v 56 Avaanu vinshi vakhandi viihumya uwulunjikhaaji wa wudehi kwa Yeesu, leelo uwulunjikhaaji waanave, wusikhandi wuhwanana.
\p
\v 57 Baheene avaanu avanji vayiima, vaava vilogola isa wudehi viija,
\v 58 “Ose tamupulikhaga umuunu uyu ilogola iijova, ‘One nisiyibomole inanda iyi iya Nguluvi yina yisenjiilwe na vaanu. Khanji mu nsiku sitatu nisiyisenje iyinji yina yisisengwa na vaanu.’”
\v 59 Leelo hata ndeeno uwulunjikhaaji waanave woope, wusikhandi wuhwanana.
\p
\v 60 Baheene umutambule umukhome wáyiima paakhati pa vaanu, wámuposa uYeesu wáaja, “Wuli, usikivagomosesa hata liswi lyolyona? Usipulikha avaanu ava vikikujova shi?”
\v 61 Leelo uYeesu wásisimaga tototo, asikhayanshile lyolyona. Umutambule umukhome wámuposa khanji wáaja, “Wuli, owe yuuwe Mukulusaaji,\f + \fr 14:61 \fq Mukulusaaji: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. Yimba iliswi \fqa Kilisito\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa. \f* Lusawo lwa Nguluvi yuna iitunwa?”
\v 62 UYeesu wámugomosesa wáaja, “Eena yuune. Khanji mukhamwaga uLusawo lwa Muunu akheele ulubali lwa kundiilo\f + \fr 14:62 \fq Ulubali lwa kundiilo: \ft Uluganulo lwakwe, uYeesu akhapeelwa ingufu nu wutawulilwa. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Sabuli 110:1. \f* lwa Nguluvi, uMunya Ngufu Soona na mukhamwaga iyinsa mu mafunde.”\f + \fr 14:62 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Daniyeli 7:13. \f*
\p
\v 63 Umutambule umukhome wáganaga kipulikha amaswi ago, wádeemula umwenda gwakwe kiwonensa inkhalasi wáaja, “Tisakula avalunjikhaaji vaashi khanji?
\v 64 Yuumwe mwapulikha shina itofola, ikiyiviikha umwene yu Lusawo lwa Nguluvi! Lino, mwijova wuli ulwa muunu uyu?” Ilivansa lyona lyalamula kiija, isakulwa abudwe.
\v 65 Baheene avanji vayansa kimufuunyila amata. Vamudinda ameeho, vamutova ni mfunsi, vamuposa vaajova, “Kuva amalago, yu naani yuna wákutova!” Avayangalilaaji woope vamutoola, vamutova na makhoofi.
\s UPetulo ikimukhaana uYeesu
\r (Mataayo 26:69-75; Luuka 22:56-62; Yohana 18:15-18, 25-27)
\p
\v 66 UYeesu pina akhandi mu nanda, uPetulo wáali apikheele pansi bahala pa lukeeke. Wáyinsa umuhinja umusenga nsengo wa mutambule umukhome.
\v 67 Wáganile kimwaga uPetulo iyoota umooto, wámungʼalulila ameeho wáaja, “Na yuuwe ukhandi lumo nu Yeesu uwa ku Nasaleti.”
\v 68 UPetulo wákhaana wáaja, “Nisimumeenye, khanji nisigameenye ago gina wilogola!” Wáwuushile wáaluta wáyiima pa mulyango sha mukhati mu lukeeke. Apo injogolo yaavikha.
\p
\v 69 Umusenga nsengo yula wámwaga khanji uPetulo, wáyansa khanji kivajova avaanu vina vaali vayiimile pala, “Umuunu uyu woope munyaayumo na vala.”
\v 70 UPetulo wákhaana khanji. Lwaganile kishila uluhaavi ludoodo, avaanu vina vaali vayiimile pala vamujovela uPetulo vaaja, “Shiyooli owe uli muyaanave wa vaanu awo, kwa kiiva na yuuwe uhumile ku Galilaya.”
\v 71 UPetulo wáyansiise kikhaana na kiyiyiiga iijova, “Nisimumeenye umuunu uyo yuna mulogola!”
\p
\v 72 Baaho injogolo yaavikha ulwa wuvili. Baheene, uPetulo wálikumbukha iliswi lila lina uYeesu wálogolaga kiija, “Pina yisinaavishe injogolo ulwa wuvili, owe usiive wanikhaana mala khatatu.” UPetulo wáganile kikumbukha ago, wáyansa kikhoola mandu.
\c 15
\s UYeesu iihigwa kwa Pilaato
\r (Mataayo 27:1-2, 11-14; Luuka 23:1-5; Yohana 18:28-38)
\p
\v 1 Kwaganile kiisha hela, ilivansa lyona ilya vatambule avakhome na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa lumo na vakhome va Vayahuudi, vapulinkhana kimusitaakha. Vamupinya uYeesu ni pingo, vamutwala kwa Pilaato, umunjaajila wa Shiluumi, kiija ahigwe.
\v 2 UPilaato wámuposiise uYeesu, “Wuli, owe yuuwe Mutwa wa Vayahuudi?” UYeesu wámugomosesa wáaja, “Owe walogola.”
\p
\v 3 Avatambule avakhome valogolaga injowo nyinshi isa kimusitaakha uYeesu.
\v 4 Baheene uPilaato wámuposa khanji wáajova, “Kwashi usiyankha lyolyona? Loleela avaanu ava shina vilogola injowo nyinshi isa kikusitaakha.”
\v 5 Leelo uYeesu asikhavagomoseese hata liswi limo. Baheene uPilaato wáswijile.
\s UPilaato ikivaposa kiija avadindulile naani
\r (Mataayo 27:15-21; Luuka 23:13-19; Yohana 18:39-40)
\p
\v 6 Shila mwakha, uluhaavi lwa shiwungo sha Pasaakha, uPilaato akhandi ana ngʼoma iya kivadindulila umudindilwa yumo, yuna avaanu vamulombaga.
\v 7 Wáali akwali umuunu yumonga yuna wáali itambulwa Balaaba, uyo wádindilwagwa lumo na vaanu avanji, kiiva vabudaga vaanu pina vatovalilanaga iselekhaali.
\v 8 Ishipuga sha vaanu shamulutiile uPilaato kilomba kiija, avagahile ngaja shina yikhandi ingʼoma yaakwe mu lusiku lwa Pasaakha.
\p
\v 9 UPilaato wávaposa kiija, “Musakula nivadindulile uMutwa wa Vayahuudi?”
\v 10 UPilaato wájovile ndeeno kiiva wáali ameenye kiija, avatambule avakhome vamutwala uYeesu kwa mwene kwa kiiva vakhandi vana jiila.
\v 11 Baheene avatambule avakhome vavafundaga avaanu woona kiija vamulombe uPilaato, avadindulile uBalaaba.
\s UYeesu iihigwa kiija vamubude
\r (Mataayo 27:22-26; Luuka 23:20-25; Yohana 19:1-16)
\p
\v 12 UPilaato wávaposa khanji wáaja, “Nimugahe shishi umuunu uyu yuna mwijova Mutwa wa Vayahuudi?”
\v 13 Avaanu woona valyova vaaja, “Umukhomeelele pa musalaaba!”
\v 14 UPilaato wávaposa khanji wáaja, “Umuunu uyu wáagaha luvi lushi?” Leelo aveene vashilile kilyova viijova, “Umukhomeelele!”
\p
\v 15 UPilaato wávadindulila uBalaaba, kwa kiiva akhandi isakula kishishendeefya ishipuga sha vaanu. Baheene wávalajisa avasulukhali vaakwe kiija, vamutove uYeesu na majalidi na kimukhomeelela pa musalaaba.
\s Avasulukhali vikimubeda uYeesu
\r (Mataayo 27:27-31; Yohana 19:2-3)
\p
\v 16 Avasulukhali vamutwala uYeesu mukhati mu mbalino ya munjaajila uPilaato, baheene avasulukhali woona vakungaana.
\v 17 Vamufwasa inkhansu induhupafu iya wutwa, vaatava injoola ya mimfwa, baheene vamufwasa pa mutwe.
\v 18 Vayansa kimuhunjila kwa mabedo viijova, “Aaje senga Mutwa wa Vayahuudi!”
\v 19 Vakhandi vikimutova ku mutwe ni lilansi na kimufuunyila amata, vakhandi vikimufugamila uYeesu na kimusungamila kwa wumyansi.
\v 20 Avasulukhali awo vaganile kimubeda na kimuneenela, vamuyaawula inkhansu induhupafu, vamufwasa khanji amenda gaakwe. Baheene vamuhumya kunja, vaaluta kimukhomeelela pa musalaaba.
\s UYeesu ikhomeelelwa pa musalaaba
\r (Mataayo 27:32-44; Luuka 23:26-43; Yohana 19:17-27)
\p
\v 21 Pina vakhandi mu nsila, vatangaanaga nu muunu yumonga yuna akhandi itambulwa Simoni, yuna akhandi mukhaaya wa lijumbi lya Kileene. Umuunu uyo wáhumile ku magunda iiluta ku Yelusalemu. Uyo akhandi wiihe wa Alekisanda nu Lufo. Avasulukhali vamukhamiilisa kisumula umusalaaba gwa Yeesu.
\v 22 Baheene vamutwala uYeesu pina pitambulwa Goligota, uluganulo lwakwe, Lipangalasi lya Mutwe.
\v 23 Vaganile kifikha, vamupeela idivaayi iya masabiibu inyansikhanie nu mugoda guna guwuusa uwuvafi, leelo umwene wákhaana kiingʼwa.
\v 24 Baheene vamukhomeelela uYeesu pa musalaaba, vagavana amenda gaakwe kwa lulagusanio, valamule kiija yu naani atoole mwenda mushi.
\p
\v 25 Yikhandi mu lisala lya wutatu ulwamilaawu, pina vamukhomeleele.
\v 26 Pashaanya pa musalaaba vakhomeleelaga ishimanyilo shina shiyandiikhwe amaswi aga kimuhiga kiija,
\qc “\sc Uyu yumwene Mutwa wa Vayahuudi\sc*.”
\p
\v 27 Vamukhomelelaga uYeesu pa musalaaba lumo na vapokhaaji vavili, shila muunu pa musalaaba gwakwe. Yumo ulubali lwa kundiilo, uyunji ulubali lwa kunshiji. [\v 28 Amaswi aga goona gasenjekhaga kikwisa gina gayandiikhwe mu Mayandikhwa aManofu kiija, “Avasiiwe lumo na vahiiji.”]\f + \fr 15:28 \ft Amaswi aga, gakusiina mu mayandikhwa agamonga amakuulu. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Isaaya 53:12.\f*
\p
\v 29 Avaanu vina vakhandi viishila mu nsila vikimwaga uYeesu pa musalaaba, vakhandi videgensa amatwe gaanave na kimusala, vakhandi viijova, “Owe ukhajovile kiija ukhayibomola inanda iya Nguluvi na kiyisenga khanji kwa nsiku sitatu,
\v 30 lino, yikulusa yuuwe, yiikha pa musalaaba!”
\p
\v 31 Shiisho ndeeno avatambule avakhome na vamanyisaaji va ndaji sa Musa vakhandi vikimubeda uYeesu viijova, “Uyu wávakulusaaga avanji, leelo igombola kiyikulusa yumwene!
\v 32 Nda yu Mukulusaaji,\f + \fr 15:32 \fq Mukulusaaji: \ft Kwa Shiyunaani yiyandiikhwe \fqa Kilisito\fqa*. Yimba iliswi \fqa Kilisito\fqa* mu Maswi aMahensa.\f* uMutwa wa Vaisilaheli, timwaje ayiishe pa musalaaba, baheene na yuuse timuhuviilile.” Avaanu vina vakhomelelwagwa lumo nu Yeesu, woope vakhandi vikimuliga.
\s UYeesu iifwa pa musalaaba
\r (Mataayo 27:45-56; Luuka 23:44-49; Yohana 19:28-30)
\p
\v 33 Kihuma ilisala lya mutanda paminsi mbakha ilisala lya gonja, inshiisi yagubikhaga inyi yila yoona.
\v 34 Baheene mu lisala lya gonja, uYeesu wákhosiise mandu ishawuti wáaja, “\tl Eloyi! Eloyi! Lama sabakhitani?\tl*” Uluganulo lwakwe, “Nguluvi wangu! Nguluvi wangu! Kwashi wanilekha?”\f + \fr 15:34 \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya Sabuli 22:1.\f*
\v 35 Avaanu vamonga vina vakhandi vayiimile pala, vaganile kipulikha ulo vaajova, “Puliisi vayaa! Ikimushemeela umukuwamalago uEliya!”\f + \fr 15:35 \fq UEliya: \ft Uyo ilogolwa apa kwa kiiva aVayahuudi vinshi vakhandi vihuviilila kiija uEliya asikhafwile kaa, leelo uNguluvi wámutoolaga mu nyi pina ali muumi na kiluta nawo kushaanya. Khanji vakhandi vaheepile kiija, uEliya akhayinsa khanji mu nyi. \xt Yimba mu litaafili lya 2 Vatwa 2:11; Malaaki 4:5.\f*
\v 36 Umuunu yumonga wáaluta luvilo, wájabikha ulupembo mu divaayi inkhali, wáviikha mu lulansi wámuvejesesa uYeesu pa mulomo angʼwele, wáaja, “Muleshi timwaje nda uEliya asiyinse kimuyiisa pa musalaaba apo!”
\p
\v 37 Baheene uYeesu wákhoosa mandu ishawuti, wáafwa.
\v 38 Uluhaavi luulo, umwenda\f + \fr 15:38 \fq Umwenda: \ft Umwenda ugu gugwene gwabagulaga mbali sivili mu nanda ya Nguluvi. Ulubali lumo Panofu, ulubali ulunji Panofu pa Panofu.\f* guna gukhandi gubagwile mbali sivili mu nanda ya Nguluvi, gwadeemukha paakhati kihuma kushaanya mbakha pansi, gwabagunkhana mbali sivili.\fig |CN01843C.jpg|col|||Umwenda ugwa nanda ya Nguluvi gudeemukha|15:38\fig*
\v 39 Umuyimililaaji wa vasulukhali, yuna akhandi ayiimile nkholeela pa Yeesu, wáganile kimwaga shina iifwa wáajova, “Shiyooli umuunu uyu akhandi Lusawo lwa Nguluvi!”
\p
\v 40 Pina gisenjekha goona aga, vaali vakwali avashimaayi vina vayiimile patali padoodo viloleela. Mu vashimaayi awo, wáali akwali uMaliya uwa ku Magidala, uSalome nu Maliya umaayi wa Yoose nu Yaakobo umunangʼana.
\v 41 Ava vaveene vikimufwataga na kimusenjela uYeesu, pina akhandi ku Galilaya. Kukhandi na vashimaayi avanji vinshi vina valutaga nu Yeesu ku Yelusalemu.
\s UYeesu iviikhwa mu lijooja
\r (Mataayo 27:57-61; Luuka 23:50-56; Yohana 19:38-42)
\p
\v 42 Ishaamihe isha lisiku ilyo ilya Ijumaa, likhandi lisiku lya kilingaania iSabaato\f + \fr 15:42 \fq ISabaato: \ft Kwa Vayahuudi yikhandi yiyansa pa Ijumaa pashaamihe.\f* ya Vayahuudi, iya kifuunya na kituuya.
\v 43 Baheene wáyinsa uYusufu yuna wáhumile mu lijumbi lya Alimataaya, yuna akhandi itiilwa mu shipuga sha vakhome va livansa. Uyo, akhandi iheepaga kiyinsa kwa Wutwa wa Nguluvi. Wáyikhangasaaga, wáaluta kwa Pilaato, wálomba umufimba gwa Yeesu, kiija alute agusiile.
\v 44 UPilaato wáganile kipulikha kiija uYeesu wáafwa, wáswijile mandu. Wámushemeela umukhome wa shipuga sha vasulukhali ligana wámuposa, nda shiyooli uYeesu wáafwa.
\v 45 UPilaato pina wápuliishe kiija uYeesu wáafwa, wámutawula uYusufu kigutoola umufimba gwa Yeesu.
\p
\v 46 Baheene uYusufu wáagula umwenda gwa kimusiilila uYeesu. Wáguyiisa umufimba gwa Yeesu pa musalaaba, baheene wámunielenga umwenda gwa kimusiilila. Wáguviikha mu lijooja lina likhandi lihimbe mu shidunda,\f + \fr 15:46 \fq Lijooja lina likhandi lihimbe mu shidunda: \ft Ingʼoma ya Vayahuudi ya kisiila avaanu, vakhandi vikivaviikha vina vafwile mu lijooja lina likhandi lihimbe mu shidunda na kiviikha ilingʼanga pa mulyango.\f* wálibiilusa ilingʼanga ilikhome pa mulyango gwa lijooja, wádinda.
\v 47 UMaliya uwa ku Magidala nu Maliya umaayi wa Yoose, vapaajile pina vagusiilile umufimba gwa Yeesu.\fig |DN00494b.jpg|span|||Kisiilwa kwa Yeesu|15:47\fig*
\c 16
\s Kifyukha kwa Yeesu
\r (Mataayo 28:1-8; Luuka 24:1-12; Yohana 20:1-10)
\p
\v 1 Lyaganile kishila ilijuva lya Sabaato, uMaliya uwa ku Magidala, uSalome nu Maliya umaayi wa Yaakobo, vagulile amafuta amanofu kiija valute vagususuute umufimba gwa Yeesu.
\v 2 Ilisiku ilya Nguluvi palwamilaawu, pina ilijuva liyansa kidibula, vaaluta ku lijooja lya Yeesu.
\v 3 Pina vakhandi mu nsila vayansa viposania veene viija, “Lino, yu naani yuna asitubilusise ilingʼanga lila pa mulyango gwa lijooja?”
\v 4 Ilingʼanga lila likhandi likhome mandu. Vaganile kifikha, valyaga ilingʼanga libilusiiwe.
\p
\v 5 Pina vayinjiile mukhati mu lijooja, vamwaga umujeleelu afwalile amenda mavalafu, akheele ulubali lwa ndiilo ulwa lijooja. Baheene avashimaayi vala, vaswijile mandu.
\v 6 Baheene umujeleelu uyo wávajovela wáaja, “Musikhatiilaji. Mukimusakula uYeesu uwa ku Nasaleti yuna vamukhomelelaga pa musalaaba? Wáfyukha, akwasiina apa! Loleeli pina vaava vamugoniise.
\v 7 Lino lutaji muvajovele avamanyisiwa vaakwe, mandu uPetulo, kiija wálongola kiluta ku nyi ya Galilaya. Ukho kukwene kuna musimwaje ngaja shina wávajovelaga.”
\v 8 Vaganile kipulikha ago, vaswiga na kitetema, vaahuma mu lijooja, vawuukha viisiga. Vasikhamujoveele umuunu yoyoona, kwa kiiva vatiilaga mandu.
\s UYeesu itwiwukha kwa Maliya uwa ku Magidala
\r (Mataayo 28:9-10; Yohana 20:11-18)
\p [\v 9 Ilisiku ilyo ilya Nguluvi ulwamilaawu, uYeesu wáganile kifyukha, wámutwiwushilaga tangusiina uMaliya uwa ku Magidala, yuna wámuwusiise amalungu fungati.
\v 10 Woope wáaluta kivajovela vala vina vakhandi lumo nu Yeesu pina asinaafwe. Uluhaavi lula vakhandi vikimukhoola uYeesu.
\v 11 Leelo vaganile kipulikha kwa Maliya uwa ku Magidala kiija, wámwaga uYeesu muumi, vasikhamuhuviliile.
\s UYeesu itwiwukha ku vavanda vavili
\r (Luuka 24:13-35)
\p
\v 12 Ulusiku lulula, uYeesu wátwiwukhaga ku vavanda vaakwe vavili mu nsila. Avavanda awo, vaali vahumile ku Yelusalemu viiluta mu njinji isa nkholeela. Vagombolaga kimumanya, kwa kiiva akhandi iwonekha ali paayo.
\v 13 Woope vatinile vaaluta ku Yelusalemu vavataviilila avamanyisiwa ishumi na yumo, leelo vasikhavahuviliile.
\s UYeesu ikivatwiwushila avamanyisiwa vaakwe
\r (Mataayo 28:16-20; Luuka 24:36-49; Yohana 20:19-23; Nsengo sa Vanandeje 1:6-8)
\p
\v 14 Kuwudugo, uYeesu wávatwiwushilaga avamanyisiwa ishumi na yumo, pina vakhandi vakheele lumo viilya. UYeesu wávakhajilaga kiiva vasikhavahuviliile vina vakhamwajile pina wáfyukhaga, kwa kiiva inumbula saanave saali nyuumu.
\p
\v 15 Baheene uYeesu wávalajisa avamanyisiwa vaakwe wáaja, “Lutaji mu nyi soona muvakhome avaanu woona iMola yangu iNofu.
\v 16 Umuunu yoyoona yuna ihuviilila na kitwinisiwa, uyo akhakulusiwa. Leelo umuunu yoyoona yuna ikhaana kihuviilila, akhahigwa.
\v 17 Khanji vina vikinihuviilila vakhagaha amabikha ngaja aga, kwa litaawa lyangu vakhadaga amalungu, khanji vakhava vilogola kwa filogolo ifipya.
\v 18 Hata nda vakhate injokha kwa mawokho, awu vangʼwe uwanga wusikhavalemasa. Khanji vakhava vikivaviishila avatamu amawokho gaanave, woope vakhava viipona.”
\s UYeesu itupulwa iiluta kushaanya
\r (Luuka 24:50-53; Nsengo sa Vanandeje 1:9-11)
\p
\v 19 UMutwa uYeesu wáganaga kilogola nawo, baheene wátupulwa kiluta kushaanya, akheele ulubali ulwa kundiilo ulwa Nguluvi.
\v 20 Woope avamanyisiwa vaakwe vawuukha pala, vaaluta koona kikhoma iMola iNofu. UMutwa uYeesu akhandi isenga insengo lumo na veene, na kijinia iliswi lyakwe ilyo kwa nsila ya mabikha gina vagahaga.]\f + \fr 16:9-20 \ft Amaswi aga, gakusiina mu mayandikhwa agamonga amakuulu. \f*
